broken_generic_other_guests_friday_not_offended_1db87684	broken	Of course, what else could that be.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	101	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_weather_friday_4d2fe2da	broken	It is not the ideal weather, but there is no reason to lose sleep over it, is there?	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	110	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_background_5b9c0613	broken	There is not much to say, I am afraid.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	119	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_background_77b3c0fd	broken	I am a mechanic. I have been doing this since the end of the war.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	119	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_background_not_offended_7d8cbbbe	broken	Thank you.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	137	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_background_not_offended_c9e820cb	broken	It is not saving lives, but I like it well enough.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	137	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_background_offended_1_e61ab54d	broken	Well yes, I was a famous actor before.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	148	broken "[what]"
