broken_generic_background_offended_2_82952855		Then he gives me a weird look.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	171	"[what]"
broken_generic_heroic_act_19cb6610	broken	Well, I suppose it is related to what I did in the war.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	182	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_heroic_act_ae1fa4e8	broken	But there were a lot of heroic acts that happened at that time.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	182	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_heroic_act_b56eb771	broken	I am not sure mine was particularly exceptional.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	182	broken "[what]"
broken_generic_heroic_act_85f7ed26	broken	I suppose I am here for a different reason.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	182	broken "[what]"
