broken_generic_room_offended_8a07fdae	doctor	From what I remember, Shakespeare paints him as a man twisted both in body and in soul.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	381	doctor "[what]"
broken_generic_room_offended_589d8062	doctor	The most impressive thing about the play was how the actor managed to convey Richard's deformity.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	381	doctor "[what]"
broken_generic_room_offended_71c90a81	doctor	His crooked posture, the twisted arm, the limp — all brought vividly to life upon the stage.	game/scripts/broken/broken_generic_choices.rpy	381	doctor "[what]"
