doctor_day2_evening_reason_drunk_silent_9cdc5b58	captain	We shall have Mr Manning taken to his room for the time being.	game/scripts/doctor/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	297	captain "[what]"
doctor_day2_evening_reason_drunk_silent_5e6d2ac8	captain	Will you assist me, Mr Harring?	game/scripts/doctor/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	297	captain "[what]"
