lad_day1_evening_3d5057ec		Going back to my room is probably the best thing to do.	game/scripts/lad/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	303	"[what]"
lad_day1_evening_8eb87d82		I hurry to my room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	315	"[what]"
