lad_day2_breakfast_eat_42de7c1f	lad	We should probably talk about something else.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	166	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_8bfa4b59		Well, I do not know if this is my best idea.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	30	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_9bf1e8b8		But I suppose it did not feel right to stay behind with the ladies.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	30	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_8f6abc5f	butler	So, this is your first hunt, Mr Harring?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	38	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_5382395a	lad	Yes. I must admit that I don't even know how to use a rifle.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	42	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_7970ae04	butler	Not to worry, sir. A footman will follow you and will reload the gun for you.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	46	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_df82b4c6	butler	All you have to do is point at your target when you encounter something and pull the trigger.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	46	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_d5f735af	lad	All right, that sounds easy enough. Will everyone have a footman as well?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	52	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_d8e2a0ea	butler	It will be just you, I believe. I will be with Lady Claythorn, and the others insisted they didn't need help.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	56	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_9a845704		Of course. So I shall be the weak link today. Brilliant.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	60	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_aa279f6c	lad	I see. And what kind of animal are we hunting today?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	64	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_bd86a589	butler	I think we will mostly encounter wild birds. But we might also run into some rabbits or even deer.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	68	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_b61e7546	lad	Aren't those dangerous?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	72	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_13e5d613	butler	Not if you don't get too close to them. And again, you won't be alone, so there's no reason to be scared.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	76	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_0466d9ae	lad	I am not scared, just curious.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	80	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_28b0fb2f	butler	Right.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	84	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_c9b3c630	butler	Anyway, you can pick up this gun and wear the clothes I laid out on the table.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	84	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_23629b96	butler	Join the others outside when you're ready.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	84	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_52918af4	lad	Perfect, thanks.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	92	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_42ca42b6		I try on the clothes laid out for me. They fit perfectly.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	96	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_34e82937		If something happens to me, at least I will look good.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	96	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_fc469947		I join the others in the garden.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_a0eeb261		They all look perfectly at ease in their hunting clothes.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_d733916a		There is Doctor Baldwin, Sushil Sinha, Lady Claythorn and her staff.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_da832ed7		And even Samuel Manning is present.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_7afba655		Wait, what?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_ac797d27		How on earth was he allowed to join us?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_6557c1e7		I approach the butler.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_98d7fca1	lad	Is it okay for Mr Manning to have a gun? He seemed a bit drunk this morning.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	120	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_a9af4f57	butler	I was concerned about that at first too. But I just spoke to him, and I can assure you he's perfectly fine.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	124	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_516afa94	butler	He might have been a bit off because of yesterday, but the breakfast and the events of this morning must have sobered him up.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	124	butler "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_18a55208	lad	All right, if you're sure.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	130	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_bf405ef2		Still, I'd better stay away from him.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	134	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_bb6a9c1a		People agree, and Sushil Sinha asks to partner with our host.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_f630a1a3		The drunk man insists on going with the doctor, who reluctantly agrees.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_3d87e56e		I am the odd one out.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_e8e037a8		Which group should I join?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_be6ee125		Despite the risks, I decided to follow Doctor Baldwin and Samuel Manning.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_b991321b		At least this way, I probably won't be the one embarrassing myself.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_88307f66		We walked for a while without encountering anything.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_3f0ad2a8		Then, we decided to stop for luncheon.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_536359c6		The four of us sat down in a clearing, sharing a small picnic.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_5edd37b1		Mr Manning is silent, busy drinking from a pocket flask.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_47e740e7		He looks serious, even nervous.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_dc48dd8c		As usual, the footman says nothing.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_af08c6ba		That means the doctor and I are the only ones talking.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_962fa6fe	doctor	So, Mr Harring, how are you finding it here?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	31	doctor "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_43a07122	doctor	It's a lovely place they have, isn't it?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	31	doctor "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_8894207b	lad	Certainly. It's a refreshing change of scenery for me.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	37	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_bf3f63c4	lad	I don't often get to see nature like this.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	37	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_e3cc269b	doctor	Ah, so you're a city chap.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	43	doctor "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_568bcd14	doctor	London?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	43	doctor "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_d4fce9b4	lad	Birmingham. I was born and raised there.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	49	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_4de30421		But I don't really want to talk about that.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	55	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_ee095666		Let's change the subject.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	55	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_e95e90a8		Our lunch is coming to an end.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	67	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_05a1a82c	footman	Alright, if everyone's ready, we can continue.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	71	footman "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_097dc975	footman	Hopefully, we'll have better luck this time.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	71	footman "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_d259a552		For a while, we didn't.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_06ced1d3		But then I spotted something that looked like a rabbit in the distance.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_e42ac0f7		Doctor Baldwin was ahead of me and didn't notice.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_ac737422		I point out my prey to the footman, and he nods in approval.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_994d53d8		So, I get into an aiming position.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_537a6c22		But as soon as I do, Samuel Manning, who was behind me, sees what's happening.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_e3880392		He coughs up blood.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	95	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_8fba9551		And then, silence.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	95	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_9436c9b9		After a while, the footman returns with the others.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	105	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_c2455c33		By the time they get here, it's too late.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	105	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_accident_9e340499		Doctor Baldwin has bled out, and he lies lifeless in the forest.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2a_accident.rpy	105	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_fea60584		Following our hostess seemed to be the safest course of action.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_5ba0028e		The only problem is that both she and Sushil Sinha are completely in their element.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_22c2a9c6		While I clearly am not.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_3d46a878		They've already shot a few rabbits and a pheasant.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_5be45637		Out of pity, they even tried to help me shoot a deer that crossed my path.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_d86bed10		However, I merely managed to scare the animal away.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	9	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_60352b13	captain	Tough luck, Mr Harring. I'm sure you'll get the next one.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	23	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_8ae559b5	lad	Thank you, but I don't think this is for me. I believe I missed it by several feet.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	27	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_febbdc11	captain	Don't fret, you just lack practice.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	31	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_f79dbbe5	captain	Then again, it might be for the best. You wouldn't have wanted to serve in the war.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	31	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_cd4af849	captain	It was truly brutal. Nothing like the previous conflicts I participated in.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	31	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_f204ff27	lad	Have you fought in many wars?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	39	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_8f850b98	captain	Indeed, I began my career in India and encountered my first battle during the war with Burma.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	43	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_ecb9e7fd	captain	I was also involved in the Chinese rebellion of the Boxer's. Then ...	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	43	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_baf3a93d		Our conversation about the wars seemed to make Lady Claythorn uneasy, as she suddenly interrupts us.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	51	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_2cb0103d	host	Well, I believe it's time for luncheon. How would you feel about settling here for our picnic?	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	55	host "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_083a855d	captain	Yes, it's a perfect spot.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	59	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_29e41d2a		We began setting up the picnic.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	65	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_1180048f		However, before we could start eating, we heard a gunshot nearby.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	71	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_d8721bcb	captain	Ah, it sounds like the others have caught something. And they're not far from here.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	75	captain "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_78156140		But soon after the gunshot, another sound followed.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_52d11435		A desperate cry for help.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_8daaa8ec		The captain and I heard it, immediately jumping to our feet.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_11146098		We rushed in the direction of the cry.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_b7571fd1		Soon, we came upon the others.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	93	"[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_555c0045		Doctor Baldwin is on the ground.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	93	"[what]"
