lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_27fd3d03	drunk	It was an accident.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	101	drunk "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_noaccident_2adc6b67	drunk	I can't believe this happened.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2a_Hunt/2b_noaccident.rpy	101	drunk "[what]"
