lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_1c25277f	lad	Really? That's fascinating.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	40	lad "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_334fa982	psychic	Yes, but so as not to bore Miss Marsh, I shall not go into the details again.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	44	psychic "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_af782ef2	psychic	If you're interested, we can discuss it another time.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	44	psychic "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_6af11948	nurse	Anyway, you mentioned being concerned about the man who died last night.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	50	nurse "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_67607c67	psychic	That is correct. I have a feeling there is something amiss about his death.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	54	psychic "[what]"
