lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_9cbd0bac	psychic	That area isn't somewhere we should wander into, Mr Harring.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	90	psychic "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_7fd877a0	psychic	Regardless, there are probably many staff members you haven't met yet.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	90	psychic "[what]"
