lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_f767fddd	psychic	Aren't you the maid? I thought I saw you tidying my room earlier.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	139	psychic "[what]"
lad_day2_hunt_tea_room_7db3d259	maid	Well, ... the truth is, I am the cook. But I occasionally assist as a maid when needed.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/2b_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	147	maid "[what]"
