lad_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_hypothesis_drunk_5227871b	lad	I doubt that Samuel Manning was truly drunk at the time of the accident.	game/scripts/lad/Day 2/3_Evening/2b_billiard_room.rpy	92	lad "[what]"
