lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_4f0daf3a	psychic	This is Samuel Manning's room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	776	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_5337d243	lad	Mr Manning?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	782	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_65a11d85	lad	Are you in there?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	782	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_3512255f		No answer.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	788	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_d94b0a4e	lad	The door's locked anyway.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	792	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_drunk_26698748	lad	Mr Sinha has the key.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	792	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_psychic_5987f775	psychic	Why are we in my room?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	804	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_psychic_5e651b2d	psychic	Surely you don't think someone's hiding here?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	804	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_psychic_bcc1206a	lad	Probably not, but it's wise to be thorough.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	810	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_psychic_4612039f		But she is right.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	814	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_psychic_15593824		The room is empty.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	814	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_doctor_061c0869		I'm back in Daniel Baldwin's room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	826	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_doctor_61243eca		His lifeless body still lies on the bed.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	826	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_doctor_c55b7021		Aside from that, everything seems in order.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	826	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_doctor_2ce18430		I don't wish to linger here any longer than necessary.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	826	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_broken_6dd62d71		I'm in Thomas Moody's room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	844	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_broken_def67b1e		He is still lying on the bed.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	844	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_broken_c2666a89		I see no one else around.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	844	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_bedroom_broken_61f6cbcf		I should move on.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/0_map_choices.rpy	844	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_91168ded		I am awaken by the sound of frantic knocking at the door.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_59a9dc89		My head is throbbing.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	43	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_80ac2e2a		I wish I could've slept longer.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	43	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_ec85bbed	psychic	Mr Harring, are you there?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	49	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_50870891		Miss Baxter?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	55	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_d8a16f61		Right, we agreed to wake each other up.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	55	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_518275ec		I just didn't expect it to be this early.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	55	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_149782a1		Miss Baxter, again?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_de3ec41d		What does she want now?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_74cf0e24	lad	I'm coming!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	72	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_95ef5e39		I hastily dress and open the door.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	76	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_6ed2149f	lad	Miss Baxter, is everything okay?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	80	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_dbe592b1	psychic	I'm not sure.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	86	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_9ae4a844	psychic	Something unusual seems to be happening.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	86	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_ac426677	psychic	I woke up early as always and wanted to get a cup of tea before breakfast.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	86	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_c084d72c	psychic	But, there's no one around.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	86	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_5bc886f2	lad	What do you mean?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	96	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_0d577856	psychic	The staff is missing. Every single one of them.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	100	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_b0d105a3	psychic	I searched everywhere - the kitchen, outdoors, everywhere.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	100	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_0ad06aa2	psychic	I haven't found anyone.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	100	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_d7b6da64	lad	Perhaps they're still sleeping?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	108	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_92913193	psychic	Oh, Mr Harring, that's highly unlikely.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	112	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_84e8728a	psychic	They're usually up at dawn, preparing the house for the day.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	112	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_e1c55a97	psychic	It's inconceivable that they all overslept.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	112	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_6890bdc4	psychic	Moreover, I tried checking on Lady Claythorn, but she's not answering.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	112	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_87b789e1	lad	Try not to worry too much. I'm sure there's a reasonable explanation.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	122	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_063c9fc0	psychic	I'm not so sure.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	126	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_9d028e2e	psychic	But I don't want to continue my search alone.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	126	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_edcdc5e1	psychic	Would you accompany me to check on the others?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	126	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_d5e6602f	lad	Well, since I'm up, I might as well.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	134	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_014004d7	lad	If it helps put your mind at ease.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	134	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_8e6a1074		We decide it's best to check each room together.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_5bac3acc		So, we start with...	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	140	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_cb9aaf95		I doubt we'll find anyone now.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	162	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_affae98c		So we settled in the tea room to wait for Captain Sinha.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	162	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_3eaf3409	captain	It's unbelievable, but it seems we're the only three living souls left here.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	168	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_4e304796	captain	Did you find anything?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	168	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_686b2eca	lad	Nothing.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	174	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_3817d71e	lad	It seems everyone is gone.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	174	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_3d70c196	lad	Except for the bodies.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	174	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_morning_1b721dc2		Just when we started losing hope, we decided to rest in the tea room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	184	"[what]"
lad_day3_morning_03565043		But as we settled down, an authoritative voice echoed from outside the room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	184	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_43eb43db		We stayed in the tea room and gathered our strength while Sushil Sinha kept searching the manor.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	30	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_af6f8eb3		When he returned, we had started to feel a bit better.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	30	"[what]"
