lad_day3_leave_with_car_d8226d59	lad	We don't know how to drive it, but perhaps you do?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	71	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_948db31e	captain	I can drive, yes.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_077d36ac	captain	I saw the car you're talking about.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_0dabf98d	captain	I even tried to start it, but no luck.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_37604291	captain	I don't think it's broken; it's probably just out of gas.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_6f0cc3f5	captain	I couldn't find any in the garage.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_6e420348	captain	So, I'm afraid that car won't be much help.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_ac38eda3	captain	Unless either of you spotted a jerrycan somewhere in the mansion?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	77	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_83d9c106	lad	No, I haven't.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	93	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_ddb47b22	psychic	Neither have I.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	97	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_b37f1f19	captain	That's unfortunate.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	101	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_leave_with_car_9e86e5ab	captain	It seems we have no choice but to proceed on foot.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	101	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_e7399c0f		I don't feel comfortable leaving Amelia Baxter alone here.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_c7d6ec06		And in any case, I don't like the idea of being alone with this guy in the forest.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_22c42af1		For all we know, he might very well be the killer.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_4e31def0		Miss Baxter doesn't seem to trust him either.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_9e85d628		So I figure it's best for us to stay here and be on our guard.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_5aeec0ed		If we're lucky, the captain will return with reinforcements, and everything will be fine.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	7	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_a0999259	lad	I think I should stay here.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	23	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_6d933b4b	psychic	Yes! Thank you, Mr Harring.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	27	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_ba017140	captain	It's decided then, I'll go alone.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	31	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_d53d89d0	captain	And there is no time to lose, so I better leave immediately.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	31	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_3da44309	psychic	Good thinking. And don't worry about us, we'll be fine here.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	37	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_167825b6	psychic	Be careful.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	37	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_4951ad3e	lad	Good luck, Captain.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	43	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_89ef16dd	captain	Thank you both. I will be back soon.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	47	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_49fa5526		We watched him leave the room, and I can sense relief in Miss Baxter's eyes.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	51	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_d4ca5caf		As soon as Captain Sinha is out of sight, she stands up.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	51	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_4a6abe77		I accompany Miss Baxter to her room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	61	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_89838cb1	psychic	This is where we part.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	65	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_38551b28	psychic	We'll meet again in the dining room in a few minutes.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	65	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_387ebdb0	lad	Alright, see you soon.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	71	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_stay_de67901b		I see her enter her room, but as I'm about to leave for mine, a strange feeling overwhelms me.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_80d70252		Something tells me not to go to my room.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_22ac2ed4		That I should return to the dining room immediately.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	79	"[what]"
lad_day3_stay_ec012af7		What should I do?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	79	"[what]"
