lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_1dbe7c58		It feels like someone might jump out at me any moment.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	103	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_cc956152		Once I reached my room, I try not to waste any time.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	113	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_9e979121		First things first, I spend a penny.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	113	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_d598e962		Once I'm done, I rush back as quickly as possible, nearly running down the stairs.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	121	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_6907b51f		Rosalind Marsh is already at her place.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	127	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_e3463881		I sat down at my seat.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	127	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_dd5af19e		When Miss Baxter comes back, we start eating in silence.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	127	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_e46f3a5c		There's not much we want to discuss.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	127	"[what]"
