lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_17883bdd		It's just something to do while we wait.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	139	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_64266e34		But as soon as I stand up, I realise I can't stay on my feet.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	149	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_toilet_14f9b82c		My head spins, and I feel faint.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	149	"[what]"
