lad_day3_afternoon_no_toilet_ad176916		She jumps up, visibly startled.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	186	"[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_no_toilet_06f13284	nurse	Oh, nothing special. I just realised the plate set out for me is too full.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	190	nurse "[what]"
