lad_day3_afternoon_no_toilet_737a5607	nurse	But you are a strong gentleman.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	190	nurse "[what]"
lad_day3_afternoon_no_toilet_62e64b75	nurse	I am sure you won't mind switching with me, right?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2a_stay.rpy	190	nurse "[what]"
