lad_day3_escape_9fc553e5	psychic	When you come back, I might be dead.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	17	psychic surprised "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_48f73d33	captain	There's no need to be so dramatic.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	27	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_0722f6d7	captain	If you lock yourself in your room, you'll likely be safe.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	27	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_7a585681	psychic	Really? Like Mr Manning was safe?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	33	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_3938f927	captain	That's different. Samuel Manning didn't expect anyone would come for him.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	37	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_8c4c70cf	captain	He was probably killed in his sleep.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	37	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_42318022	captain	Or maybe he took his own life.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	37	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_2465a776	captain	For you, it'll be different. You'll be on your guard.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	37	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_3e52fa11	psychic	What good will that do when someone breaks down my door?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	47	psychic "[what]"
