lad_day3_escape_ce5d0262	psychic	But... I don't know how to use this!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	65	psychic "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_cf76f313	captain	It's simple. If someone breaks down your bedroom door, just point it at them and press the trigger.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	69	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_26b47991	captain	That's all there is to it.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	69	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_ea995090	psychic	I don't know if I can do that, I...	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	75	psychic "[what]"
