lad_day3_escape_86c711e0	captain	Now, go to your room and lock the door.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	79	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_9688e7de	captain	Maybe even move some furniture in front of it.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	79	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_f0e196ff	captain	If anyone other than us tries to enter, shoot them.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	79	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_f606189f	captain	Understood?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	79	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_60cca07c		Amelia Baxter is visibly terrified.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	91	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_e4497f52		But the natural authority of Sushil Sinha makes her nod in agreement.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	91	"[what]"
