lad_day3_escape_65fd3aa1		He takes out a gun from his back pocket and points it at me.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	165	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_c58eafd8	lad	What the hell?!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	169	lad surprised "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_c99c5563	captain	Oh, don't act so surprised.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_e81ebf25	captain	Did you really think you fooled me?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_ab6d5d85	captain	I spotted the gun in your pocket this morning.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_759aa78b	captain	If you were waiting for a chance to catch me off-guard, you're in for a disappointment.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_9d162fa4	lad	No! That's not what I planned, it's ...	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	183	lad surprised "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_cfd2b396		He fires at me.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_a78ec747		He misses.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_bc1ccad5		For the first time, he looks panicked.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_05afd63e		I reach for the gun in my pocket.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_34d7846c		Pointing it at him, I pull the trigger.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_0bbd36c0		But then realise it's empty.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	189	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_06ba0a6d		We had been walking for about two hours when he stops.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	210	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_8df975f2	captain	Wait!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	214	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_55d235db	captain	Did you hear that?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	214	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_f84aec51	lad	Not really.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	220	lad "[what]"
