lad_day3_escape_6f52d144	captain	I heard footsteps from the forest.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_f651c48b	captain	I think someone's following us.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_31bae647	lad	What?!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	234	lad surprised "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_b2bdc9d0	captain	Keep quiet.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	238	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_6e7417ed	captain	Pretend nothing's wrong.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	238	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_641ae071	lad	What should we do?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	244	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_41a2f0e0	lad	Should we make a run for it?	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	244	lad "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_6a7508b8	captain	No, I'll try to ambush him.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	250	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_98eb9f62	captain	I think I've pinpointed his location.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	250	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_eb09e7c3	captain	I'll charge at him.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	250	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_b0055774	captain	When I give the signal, start running on the road to divert his attention.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	250	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_f2ae7976	captain	I'll dash into the forest to try and disarm him.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	250	captain "[what]"
