lad_day3_escape_bda42d7d	captain	Go!	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	270	captain "[what]"
lad_day3_escape_bb7128ac		Before I can even think, I start running.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	284	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_029841e4		A gunshot rings out.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	290	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_42466030		I glance back to see Sushil Sinha collapsing to the ground.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	290	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_98d9b2d8		But I can't stop.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	290	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_28c91af3		My legs push me forward faster than ever before.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	290	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_7151e904		I've never run this fast in my entire life.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	290	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_0ddb7cd8		Minutes later, I'm gasping for breath.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	308	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_a2f8bf82		I'm not sprinting anymore, just jogging — barely faster than a brisk walk.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	308	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_6ffff93b		But I have to keep going.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	308	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_df79f817		I find a nearly comfortable pace and maintain it, occasionally glancing behind me.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	308	"[what]"
lad_day3_escape_c92b2a0e		Thankfully, no one is in sight.	game/scripts/lad/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	308	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_85f154fd		You don't wake up.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_4eef33c4		You have died during the night.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_ba2f12cd		It's unfair, I know.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_8938e772		You don't think that you have done anything wrong.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_f995b70b		And you probably haven't.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_ending_day1_deathbed_a0cc98c5		But sometimes, people die without knowing why.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	11	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_f9f416ac		Well, you're dead.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_963af9c9		Shot to death.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_9063ac20		And no explanation was given.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_2cdd82c9		If you feel you're owed one, think again.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_47389662		Why would someone explain to their victims why they're being killed?	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_b0c1a29e		It wouldn't make sense.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_gunned_down_ending_fcbd31d5		If you want a clearer understanding, you'll have to seek it out yourself.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	36	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_poisoned_15f92cdf		You lay on the floor, saliva dripping from your mouth.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	62	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_poisoned_75d183e1		Whatever poison you ingested is now coursing through your veins.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	62	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_poisoned_6e240e59		Let this be a lesson to you.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	62	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_poisoned_a52af4be		Never trust anyone.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	62	"[what]"
