lad_ending_day3_fell_528c3f09		You didn't stand a chance.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	84	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_fell_5a674cb2		But you were so close to escaping.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	84	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_fell_9c8a1c41		It must be incredibly frustrating.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	84	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_fell_ddf0af56		You'll need to be more cautious next time.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	84	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_7f692c96		After what felt like an eternity, I finally reached the town.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	107	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_20786932		I rushed into the police station and told them everything.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	107	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_8c066c62		I was exhausted, panicked, and probably came off as unhinged.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	107	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_81d667c8		Yet, they agreed to investigate the matter.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	107	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_e4a45da2		I was too drained and frightened to accompany them, but they told me everything when they came back.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	107	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_05023652		They discovered Sushil Sinha's body on the road, likely where I last saw him.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_49daaddb		He'd been shot in the head.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_aedea82f		At that moment, the two police officers took the situation very seriously.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_6deef94e		They rushed to Claythorn Manor.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_9bf731a1		There, they discovered that all of the remaining guests had died.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_58cf7768		Samuel Manning, Thomas Moody, and Daniel Baldwin were still in their beds.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_48bfbf14		Poor Miss Baxter was found lying lifeless in the hallway.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_f2354ee8		She didn't even make it to her room.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_c1a8d567		Rosalind Marsh was dead too.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_68d79c69		Her body was found in the attic.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_ending_day3_escape_e67e2f90		They have no idea where Lady Claythorn and her staff went.	game/scripts/lad/Endings/endings.rpy	122	"[what]"
lad_generic_room_friday_8d513fbf	lad	I don't know, I haven't been to my room yet.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	29	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_friday_f60d2ee7	lad	I just arrived, and I didn't realise I would be the last one here.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	29	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_doctor_50c5d7ba	lad	I am in the 'William the Conqueror' Bedroom.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	40	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_doctor_ee32c7c0	doctor	A glorious name.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	44	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_room_doctor_bf3c32b0	lad	I suppose.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	48	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_doctor_986764a4		He looks like he doesn't know who that was.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	52	"[what]"
lad_generic_room_doctor_0f45de5b		I should leave it at that.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	52	"[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_d82264ac	lad	Oh, I am in the "William the Conqueror" Bedroom.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	65	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_f9e88e18	psychic	An impressive king.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	69	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_411b4d19	lad	Really, he was?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	73	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_e06b438c		Is he serious?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	77	"[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_6a2ba3be		Hasn't he heard of "William the Conqueror"?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	77	"[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_b9c38f64	psychic	Well, he was a French Duke who was able to take the throne of England from very powerful men.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_68e77c3f	psychic	That's not nothing.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_982778a0	psychic	On the other hand, he was sometimes also called the Bastard King.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_room_psychic_bcbfbaf3	psychic	So make of that what you will.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_age_psychic_99c2dc2d	lad	I am 22 years old.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	100	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_age_psychic_dd916af7		That make sense, but he somewhat looks older than that.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_generic_age_psychic_c54cbdf0		I guess it's his rugged look.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_generic_age_psychic_f206d565		Life is not easy for the working class.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	104	"[what]"
lad_generic_age_99c2dc2d	lad	I am 22 years old.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	119	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_age_df97b021		He appears a touch older than that.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	123	"[what]"
lad_generic_age_1a882d34		But then, growing up through a war is enough to age anyone before their time.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	123	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_1_69ccc9fe	lad	There isn't much to say about me.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	136	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_1_81f0b4c0	lad	I was born and raised in Birmingham.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	136	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_1_c7159f16	lad	I work there as a business associate.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	136	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_228175e3	psychic	Interesting, in what type of business?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	153	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_e4e13a9e	lad	Well, just regular sales.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	157	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_32cb6ce4	psychic	And do you sell anything in particular?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	161	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_009b08cb	lad	A bit of everything, depending on the opportunities.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	165	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_49c10049	psychic	You don't have a store then?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	169	psychic "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_67d44ce8	lad	No, no, it's nothing like that.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	173	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_94f93129		He seems uneasy.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	177	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_aa8b6cac		He is probably ashamed of what he is doing.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	177	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_psychic_dce28a1d		I shouldn't push him further.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	177	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_79e026b6	doctor	In what line of business?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	194	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_caa27071	lad	Oh, you know, regular sales.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	198	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_242ba667	doctor	Of course. What do you sell the most?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	202	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_c38de194	lad	I cannot say that I work with a specific product; it depends on the opportunities.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	206	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_c9b5288c	doctor	I see.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	210	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_02588e30		There is something off about his answers.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	216	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_ffab5e8f		I do not think he is telling me the whole story.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	216	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_687bad9a		Perhaps I could probe him a little further.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	216	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_80ad93b2	lad	Really?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	235	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_1af9dffa	lad	I thought you were a doctor.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	235	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_6ebdaf5f	doctor	I am.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_e8380ea5	doctor	And because of that, I sometimes have access to certain products in large quantities.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_78e10310	doctor	Perhaps you could assist me with a small matter.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_9ca54262	lad	That depends.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	249	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_500c64bf	lad	Care to tell me a bit more?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	249	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_c6f6c2ec	doctor	Not here.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_9b472a88	doctor	It is rather sensitive.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_9ab07798	doctor	Not something meant for every ear, if you take my meaning.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_55ee110a	lad	Fair enough.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	263	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_39f81cf9	lad	I can keep my mouth shut when I need to.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	263	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_e73d0639	doctor	Excellent.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	269	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_a0528443	doctor	We shall speak again later.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	269	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_328d8e12		Interesting.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	275	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_cab957e7		He is clearly willing to take part in something rather unorthodox.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	275	"[what]"
lad_generic_background_doctor_thief_33c239c5		And it is equally clear he has done this sort of thing before.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	275	"[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_e0b1178d	lad	I was just going home one day, it was rather late.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_1cf9e43b	lad	On my way, I happened to notice smoke coming from a house across the street.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_7f60b2e8	lad	I was about to call for the firemen.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_d14e83f2	lad	But out of the window, I heard a baby screaming.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_b3c2b297	lad	I couldn't possibly stay there and do nothing.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_heroic_act_1_e0f99857	lad	So without thinking about it, I forced the front door of the house and ran upstairs.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_choices.rpy	297	lad "[what]"
