lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_2bf9bef3	doctor	He looks quite out of his wits again.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	119	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_a7648fc6	lad	Yes, I noticed he is drunk most of the time.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	125	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_73d7d6cd	lad	But that is about all I have witnessed so far.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	125	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_7d5e161c	doctor	Yes, I suppose that was obvious to everyone.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	131	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_dead_666bb0a5	lad	Samuel Manning?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	142	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_dead_b221494d	lad	Well does it really matter what I think of him now?	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	142	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_dead_949e713f	doctor	No, of course not.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	148	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_dead_046f73d5	doctor	I don't know why I asked you that.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	148	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_drunk_hunt_doctor_dead_6c60e55a	doctor	I am sorry.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	148	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_captain_hunt_doctor_d0868180	lad	Captain Sinha is serious, and he does go on about himself.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	163	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_captain_hunt_doctor_6a5a0aa1	doctor	I have observed the same.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	167	doctor "[what]"
lad_generic_host_hunt_doctor_16c72fa6	lad	She is very distinguished.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	178	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_host_hunt_doctor_2c269cb9	lad	I have not dared to speak to her yet.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	178	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_nurse_hunt_doctor_149886e8	lad	I do not have much to say about her.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	191	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_nurse_hunt_doctor_d6855187	lad	She is a rather discreet woman, so I have not learnt much about her.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	191	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_broken_hunt_doctor_54db5588	lad	Poor Mr Manning, it is creepy to imagine he is still in his room.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	204	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_broken_hunt_doctor_d369b44e	lad	You know, dead.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	204	lad "[what]"
lad_generic_broken_hunt_doctor_8f3bb949	doctor	That is how we left him, so I daresay his condition has not changed.	game/scripts/lad/lad_generic_other_guests.rpy	210	doctor "[what]"
nurse_introduction_c7eff3c0		The letter rests upon my lap.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_7ae352cf		On the surface, it is perfectly composed. Generous, even.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_0eb9cdac		A weekend at a Scottish manor, an award for distinguished service, prize money of one thousand pounds.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_9768fc46		But dig a little deeper, and one notices something is not quite right.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_9f0f7993		The vague wording. The pressure to attend in person. The promise of money that exists only provided one makes an appearance.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_ab82bedc		Everything in this letter seems to be a rather elaborate ploy to gather people in an isolated place.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_b32a53b7		The question is why.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_3367c33a		The sensible thing would have been to remain at home.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_d845e533		Yet here I am, travelling somewhere in Scotland, watching the countryside blur past the carriage window.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_641c3dc9		I fold the letter and slip it back into my handbag.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	25	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_93a9029e		The cough comes without warning, much as it always does.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_1608d4f0		I press my handkerchief to my mouth and wait for the fit to pass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_4fda6eb9		There is blood. Not much for now. That at least is mildly reassuring, though I know it shall not last.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_53b1c705		I fold the handkerchief away before anyone can notice.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_4ce080b7		The doctor gave me his assessment three months ago, in that careful, measured tone they all adopt when they have nothing comforting to say.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_446705f9		Consumption. The word sits heavy in my chest, much like the cold does now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_de2e013b		He prescribed rest. Fresh air. A sanatorium, if at all possible.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_baf272eb		A sanatorium.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_d12ce09a		I cannot afford that sort of luxury.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_3ca7b6f1		But I cannot afford to do nothing, either.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_00fbd253		So in the end, I had little choice but to attend this weekend, regardless of the risks.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_35ddded8		If there is no prize at the end of this, I will have to 'find' things of value myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_8cec2d6b		One way or another, I shall make this weekend worthwhile.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	49	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_a60e4731		As I step off the train, I scan the platform.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_db322777		Near the exit, a young man in livery is already in conversation with a gentleman.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_9e4c077a		I make my way towards them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_13bc278e		I take a seat behind the footman, leaving the two men to settle in beside me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_574f41bb		The doctor attempts conversation, and I do my part — a polite smile here, a short reply there.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_d3dd376b		But my attention keeps drifting.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_c364635d		Seven guests in total, if the letter is to be believed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_7ad71b64		A doctor. A man disfigured in the war. That is two accounted for.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_787b21f6		I wonder what links us all together.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_bed44805		By the time we turn onto a wooded track, the men have both fallen quiet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_9542dcb2		The doctor is watching the road. The soldier stares blankly out of the window.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_35aee1a8		Neither of them seems especially at ease.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_bc4b59e8		I feel a familiar tightness in my chest and breathe through it slowly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_81d9529e		A full weekend on my feet. I shall have to be rather careful about it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_6f9f85a9		If I exert myself, my health will be at risk.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_8652cc4c		But if I stay in my bed most of the time, then why come at all?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_8338dd78		It is a fine line to walk, and I must be cautious about it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_3269a120		The house comes into view just as the first drops of rain begin to fall.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_423e5d83		It is larger than I had expected. And older.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_423bed5e		The sort of house that costs more to maintain than most people earn in a lifetime.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_5763c5c4		Someone here has money — or at least the appearance of it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_06dcece2		I should have no trouble leaving with a little more than I arrived with.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_introduction_2b97445d		I straighten my coat and step out of the motorcar.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/1_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_downstairs_crowded_64d90e91		I almost go in until I notice some of the staff.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_downstairs_crowded_6ba7a6ea		They are busy cleaning today's meal.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_downstairs_crowded_fee23246		No chance of doing anything useful in there tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_downstairs_crowded_e2858ed8		The scullery will be just the same, connected as it is to the kitchen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_downstairs_crowded_f3430c31		I pull the door to and leave without anyone having noticed me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dining_room_ccf2b844		The dining room is deserted.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dining_room_80a9d3ff		The staff are clearing away the last of the dishes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dining_room_1e72d818		I receive a faintly puzzled look from the footman.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dining_room_993ae4e6		I offer no explanation and withdraw.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_garden_a8575671		I step towards the front door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_garden_aa439a9c		A draught finds its way under the frame.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_garden_4a2481cc		The weather has worsened considerably since this afternoon.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_garden_652fe9a5		I am not well enough to be wandering about in the cold and the dark.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_garden_3bf27590		I turn back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_too_dangerous_3512255f		No answer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	136	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_too_dangerous_c522102c		I could try my skills to enter anyway.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	144	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_too_dangerous_88a96c49		But that seems far too dangerous to try anything, with the house still so full of people.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	144	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_too_dangerous_ad377d07		There must be better places to explore for now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_drunk_4d94c2f6		My knocking nudges the door open a little.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	165	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_drunk_4dc8ff49		The smell that reaches me from inside is enough.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	165	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_drunk_a0ec4607		Spirits, and something stale beneath it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	165	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_drunk_b01c6321		I know better than to enter.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	165	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_dd0c5fad	psychic	Yes? Who is there, please?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	184	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_117572eb	nurse	Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	188	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_3aaee8c7	psychic	Oh, Miss Marsh. I am rather tired, I'm afraid.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	192	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_e4f11902	psychic	Could we speak tomorrow?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	192	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_25035da3	nurse	Of course. I shan't disturb you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	198	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bedroom_psychic_4510c80d	nurse	Good night.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	198	nurse "[what]"
nurse_attic_default_2e296663		The attic staircase is narrow and the floorboards announce every step.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	340	"[what]"
nurse_attic_default_72833b9d		I stop.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	340	"[what]"
nurse_attic_default_962530f6		A woman wandering uninvited through the servants' quarters would not go unremarked.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	340	"[what]"
nurse_attic_too_dangerous_7978b20e		I ought not to have come up here at all.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	353	"[what]"
nurse_attic_too_dangerous_1511a002		This is not the right moment to venture around here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	353	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_check_exhaustion_50deeaea		A wave of tiredness washes over me quite suddenly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	368	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_check_exhaustion_0d546c35		The journey here took more out of me than I thought.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	368	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_check_exhaustion_d71ccf17		If I push myself much further tonight, I shall pay for it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	368	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_05f8a4f7		As I enter, the butler steps forward to greet us.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_7c004858		The butler shows Doctor Baldwin and Thomas Moody their rooms, then we reach mine.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	37	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dabc541f	butler	Miss Marsh, you'll stay in the "Queen Alexandra Room".	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	41	butler "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_2efa5907		He opens the door to a spacious, well-appointed room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	45	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_1b12cde1	butler	Let me know if I can do anything for you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	51	butler "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_bc75a22a	nurse	Very well, thank you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	55	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_fe454c99		The journey has taken rather more out of me than I'd care to admit.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	59	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_021a24e9		I should rest before dinner.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	59	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_3d55f686		I wake up a bit refreshed — enough to face the evening.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_cdc4274e		I should go downstairs to meet the others.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_c8292484		The tea room is quieter than I expected.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	79	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_859af63c		Doctor Baldwin and Thomas Moody are deep in some hushed exchange.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	79	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_54ec5541		I pour myself a tea and keep my distance.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	79	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_8f400923		Two men enter together, though they couldn't look less alike.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	87	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_dc48dd4a		One is an Indian gentleman in military dress, upright and composed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	87	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_7a218570		The other is older — rumpled jacket, unsteady on his feet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	87	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_1786088f		The soldier crosses to Doctor Baldwin without hesitation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_87db7b80		The older man drifts toward me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_245cefba	drunk	Ah! Samuel Manning, at your... at your service.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	101	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_5f05566d		He extends a hand, misses mine by several inches, and beams at me regardless.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_93280208	nurse	How do you do, Mr Manning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	109	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_aedc81e5		I make my excuses before he can finish his next sentence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	113	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_0abbe5ac		The soldier is still with Baldwin and Moody.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	113	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_f0bd33d7		I position myself nearby and wait.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	113	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_800ab9e9		He's comparing a small scar on his back to the disfigured face of Thomas Moody.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_9aac8629		That's rather insensitive.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_c7f2d17f		He speaks on at some length about the expedition.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_3f7a2972		I listen as best I can.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_15bda009		Something about the way he talks about the Anglo-Zanzibar War is odd.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_7fbe3550		There was something specific about that conflict. Yet, I can't quite place it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_309fb32c		It is too distant in my memory.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_7ef05e35		At some point I notice Doctor Baldwin has gone quiet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_b8a9f7a2		He nods along, but his eyes are elsewhere.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_1fb0e4cd		I know that look. Something on his mind, and not the conversation in front of him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	129	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_579857d1		Two more have slipped into the room without my noticing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_c1627422		A young man and a woman in rather more elaborate dress than the occasion perhaps warrants.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_35794098		I have no time to speak to them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_d7d4fd93		The gong sounds from the corridor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	157	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_da259469		My place is set at the far end of the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_d2aecbf2		To my distinct dismay, the only person situated next to me is Mr Manning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_572ae833		Of all the guests to be seated beside, I must endure the one who can scarcely stand straight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_3dd1b14a		Once the speech concludes, the first course promptly follows.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_f830dd75		Shortly after, the staff circle the table to pour the wine.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_3559b8bc	drunk	Yes, yes — don't be stingy with it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	185	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_71f7a6e1	drunk	Thank you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	185	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_904c8444		It appears the evening will be quite as taxing as I had feared.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	191	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_206833cd		I am conflicted. If I ignore him, I might have to eat in silence, which could appear odd.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	191	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_1308e07f		But I don't know that I want to engage with him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	191	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_da38e87f		What to do?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	191	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_cf0ce9a2		Everyone is finished with dinner.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_8d56f0fa		There is talk about possible drinks after, but first I have to go to my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_66ca19d7		Before I get up, I think about the silver.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_87c0d670		It's not first rate, but I might get some money for it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_84d851fa		Should I pocket it before leaving to my room?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_fad7d95d		I stand up and go back to my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	231	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_4cbe0667		The dinner was rather taxing, so I am not sure what to do.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_b3699668		Ideally, I could search the place to find something valuable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_566c3d95		The silver is probably in the butler's pantry.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_8683062d		That could be in his bedroom, or the kitchen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_2b918703		But there could be more valuables in other places.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_040bc57c		I must keep in mind that I should not exert myself too much.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_19f6cffb		That could end badly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_30df3803		So where should I venture?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	237	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_cad3057d		It has been a long day, and the weariness has settled into my bones.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	260	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_5f06b005		I should go back to my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	260	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_c82087e4		As I reach my room, a fit of coughing takes hold — sharp and wretched.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_c7360594		I grip the bedpost until it passes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_e83ec355		I have pushed myself rather too far this evening.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_f84d339a		I change and get into bed without ceremony.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	284	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_d8e2e118		Sleep comes before I have quite decided to close my eyes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	284	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_f3ca26c0		I can't believe I am doing this.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	295	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_b45bfa1a		But It would feel too rude for me to just ignore him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	295	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_3d172bcb		And he might also take it the wrong way.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	295	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_b664cd66		It seems I have little choice	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	295	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_45ab0fd8	nurse	How are you, Mr Manning?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	305	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_fe1fd427	drunk	Me? Oh very well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	309	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_bf1411a4	drunk	The wine is first rate, you should take a sip.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	309	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_9de8a3f4		I wet my lips into it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	315	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_6b9f961c		It's barely passable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	315	"[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_25986150	nurse	Yes, it's rather good.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	321	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day1_dinner_drunk_a880a5ea		Well, what should we talk about?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	325	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_steal_b5a78b15		A quick glance to either side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_steal_c0efb821		No one is paying the slightest attention.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_steal_3ae69f5c		My hand moves before I have quite made the decision.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_steal_a3c38593		The spoon disappears into my bag with the faintest clink.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_steal_e664cc85		I take my leave before the moment passes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_do_not_steal_e7d64e02		I look at the silverware for a moment longer than I ought.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	355	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_do_not_steal_56c887cd		Then I push the thought aside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	355	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_do_not_steal_23701cc3		It is not worth the risk.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	355	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_do_not_steal_315bb47a		I rise from the table and excuse myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/1_main.rpy	355	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_c66ee002		A haze of pipe smoke hangs over the room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_2c0c4994		Captain Sinha is holding court near the fireplace.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_aa5bd84b		A small audience has gathered — the Captain's voice carries, and his stories have the weight of a man who expects to be listened to.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_619510f0		I am back in the billiard room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_5a676f45		I move a little closer to the group.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	42	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_9ebd93b1		Thomas Moody, Lady Claythorn, and Ted Harring are all listening attentively.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	42	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_f0d7bfb8		Even the butler, standing quietly in the corner, seems to be following every word.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	42	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_12b886b1	captain	Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	50	captain "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_54232c71	captain	I was just telling everyone here a story.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	50	captain "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_d34345c8	captain	Where was I?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	50	captain "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_5e9bf323	captain	Oh, right.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	50	captain "[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_e16168ad		The "Boxers"?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_c3d0975d		I remember those. That was one of my first campaigns, and perhaps the most terrible of them all.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_5564403e		Quite of a sudden, it all comes back to me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_8394544b		The crowded wards, the smell of antiseptic struggling against the heat, and a young doctor—far younger then—working tirelessly through the night.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_ebf6d10d		Daniel Baldwin.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_b5533dee		He was there. We were there, in the middle of that dreadful business.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_c7ae7ae8		I glance across the room at him, but he remains as aloof as before.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_c5c38108		Was Captain Sinha there as well? How curious that would be.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_1e739efd		I had better listen until the end.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_78b29f06		Not the worst story-teller, I will grant him that.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_9b7c0d13		But there is something that troubles me about his tale.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_bf5f6980		There was no Indian officers during that time — not at that rank.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_77ba6da8		That may well have changed after the Great War, but I am quite certain he wasn't a captain in those days.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_deb0b87a		And the claim that he was sent to London to command a training regiment — which would have been composed entirely of white men — is even more far-fetched.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_6a41647a		There is something wrong about his story.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_captain_c4dc7ac0		I should keep it in mind.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	86	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_bar_554d0598		I take a step towards the bar, then stop myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	109	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_bar_3c4bbfae		No. In my condition, a drink is quite out of the question.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	109	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_bar_41f70dc1		That was foolish to even consider it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	109	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_bar_0dc41964		I turn away before anyone notices.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	109	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_doctor_5d580338		Doctor Baldwin is sitting alone in his chair, a glass of port in hand.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	124	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_doctor_51e7502e		I make to approach him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	124	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_doctor_7ea1d9c8		But there is something in his eyes that unsettles me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	124	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_doctor_07e15137		He is distant, tired.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	124	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_doctor_f485d894		I should leave him alone.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	124	"[what]"
nurse_day1_evening_billiard_room_cancel_a2ca3632		I don't feel like staying in this room any longer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 1/2_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	143	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_69a30a20		I wake with a start and a fit of coughing seizes me before I am properly conscious.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_48c16d1d		I grip the edge of the mattress and wait for it to pass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_03e32d12		There is blood on the handkerchief. More than yesterday.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_5a7bdd1e		I fold it away and sit quietly until the dizziness fades.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_4f3cd4ea		I have been careless.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_129a0190		From now on, I must be more careful about how much I push myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_ed2089fc		I wake to a grey Scottish morning filtering through the curtains.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	50	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_f0f5644f		A moment to take stock, then I rise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	50	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_a7b8f2b4		I slept better than I feared.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	50	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_35983edf		I wash and dress methodically, whatever this day holds, it is best faced with one's wits about one.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	58	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_c8f0904d		The dining room is already partially occupied.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_52d9695f		Captain Sinha sits alone at the far end of the table, eating in his customary silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_2d8be2e4		I take a seat and help myself to some toast and tea.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_f88bb713		Amelia Baxter and Ted Harring appear and settle nearby.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_8a2cdb53		They are engaged in some conversation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_43dcdb71		Then Samuel Manning enters the room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_31d60cb9		He looks dreadful — waxy, unsteady, clutching the frame for a moment before making his way to the buffet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_2f979b34		Nobody comments on it, though I notice Miss Baxter's expression harden considerably.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_0541295d		He takes the seat beside me, bringing only a cup of black coffee—nothing to eat.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_3ddfcb3f		While he thinks I am not looking, he gets a silver flask from his pocket and pours a generous measure into his cup.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_79eedc86		Well, that settles it, I am not talking to him this morning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_e0e6a338		My gaze drifts to the other side of the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_98089f3e		Doctor Baldwin is there, composed and professional.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_485804b6		Since the Captain's story last night, the fog has lifted. I am quite certain now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_03a76f0a		It was indeed him. Though the years have added a certain weariness to his features.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_7d4ed8e5		I wonder if he recognises me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_8cf9b47a		I have a mind to ask him, but it would hardly be proper to address him from across the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_7cf4b6fc		I shall wait for a more opportune moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	92	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_213f8842		Suddenly, the butler slips into the room and bends to murmur something in Lady Claythorn's ear.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	108	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_86131c9a		Her face changes at once.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	108	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_2e75c573		She rises and crosses towards the doctor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	108	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_764ee15c		Ted Harring is rising quietly to follow them, uninvited as far as I can tell.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_132cb757		Then, the room settles into an uneasy hush.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_30c88d78		Nobody seems to know quite what to do with themselves.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_9a9777b2		The food sits barely touched on most plates.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_1863d7aa		After a while, everyone has finished eating.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	136	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_43850649		Or at any rate, has set down their cutlery and given up the pretence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	136	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_981b420f		A hunt.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_6824e7dd		I had rather forgotten about it, truth be told.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_84045004		Lady Claythorn looks at each of us in turn.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_39574ec2		A few eyebrows are raised at this.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	156	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_9da3bf16		Mr Manning looks in no fit state for a country walk, let alone a hunt.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	156	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_0a31f52f		But no one says anything aloud.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	156	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_9dfd8a62	host	Of course, I understand.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	166	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_a5015486	host	And what about you, Miss Marsh?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	166	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_e3c70bfe		I consider it for a second.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	172	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_17a60cc7		But a trudge across a cold forest , rifle in hand, would only make my condition worse.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	172	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_82c37b51		Everyone turns towards the doctor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	185	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_9eaf894a		He glances around the table with a thoughtful expression.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	185	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_0079ef65		Very well, I can return to my room now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	195	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_9d67443e		But first, my eyes settle on the silverware.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	195	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_62ed2bc8		The distraction of this morning's news has left everyone rather inattentive.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	195	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_1c545c7c		It would be easy enough.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	195	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_steal_51dcfb5e		No one is watching.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	216	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_steal_83c3cb20		My hand moves quickly and without fuss.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	216	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_steal_26d123c5		A fork disappears into my bag with the faintest clink.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	216	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_steal_a9d7a3c0		Nobody notices a thing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	216	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_do_not_steal_edd2907f		I pull my eyes away.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	233	"[what]"
nurse_day2_morning_do_not_steal_436b7c55		There has been quite enough disruption this morning without adding theft to it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	233	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_rest_before_lunch_d2b92400		I am exhausted.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	78	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_rest_before_lunch_846077a5		A quick nap before luncheon is what I need.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	78	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_early_cbbaa3dd		I do not really have the strength to explore.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_early_fcdf7c63		I should just wait for luncheon here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	95	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_downstairs_maid_da3099c7		I almost step inside until I notice one of the maids, alone.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_downstairs_maid_23a61a33		It is better if she does not see me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_downstairs_maid_63222ed5		I pull the door to and leave.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	118	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_dining_room_777707ce		The dining room is empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	134	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_dining_room_3ee62399		The table is not entirely cleared.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	134	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_dining_room_f6c05c16		Strange, that should have been done by now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	134	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_dining_room_c0718812		Looks like the manor is understaffed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	134	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_garden_5b119370		The sky is a little brighter this morning. Not much, but enough.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_garden_8ec0dfce		The paths are damp underfoot, and there is a chill still in the air, but it is pleasant to be outside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_garden_189e461e		I walk the length of the garden slowly, not pushing myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_garden_5bbdaa7b		The house is quiet behind me. It is a relief, for a moment, to be away from it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_garden_bd2f693b		I do not stay long. One circuit, and then back inside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	150	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_try_enter_fcf2f5da		With most of the household out hunting, one could easily slip inside unseen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	188	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_try_enter_9e72416c		Though it would be rather difficult to explain if I were caught.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	188	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_try_enter_65e9e481		This corridor remains quite deserted as well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	196	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_default_room_no_enter_4ccf5b09		It is best I do not go in there for now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	216	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_default_room_locked_c3919936		I try the handle gently.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	225	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_default_room_locked_88811a78		It is securely locked.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	225	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_risk_1d1b631a		Amelia Baxter is not there. This could be my best opportunity to have a look inside her room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	259	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_risk_b625cb48		But she is nearby. It will not look well if she returns and finds me here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	259	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_risk_c346e0f4		It is a considerable risk.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	259	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_3b0ae531		The door shifts slightly under my touch.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	324	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_412b4ba5		It appears Mr Manning has left it resting on the latch.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	324	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_064fd454		Since he is not coming back yet, I could take a quick look.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	324	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_35602249		I push the door open quietly, ensuring no one is watching.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	324	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_8a381f30		The room is in a frightful state.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	338	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_5de36a74		Clothes are discarded carelessly, and the unmistakable smell of spirits hangs in the air.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	338	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_e8ff648b		A brief glance reveals only empty whisky bottles.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	346	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_drunk_ab2fce30		Quite as I suspected. There is nothing of value for me here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/0_map_choices.rpy	346	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_3b43a292		I am quite content to remain behind.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_c5c9dd14		It will allow me to rest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_101c513e		Even though I should at least join Mrs Baxter for lunch.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_6b590cf1		And I could take the opportunity that most people are outside to "look" more intensively into this place.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_cd05d0b5		Obviously, the priority would be to find the stash of money promised to everyone.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_712c2435		But, if as I suspect, there isn't any, I am sure I can find other valuables.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	31	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_05405d2c		I already secured some silverware.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	47	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_c039c17f		A rather risky thing to do.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	47	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_7ccce06f		That may not help me much, but it's still something.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	47	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_4fe6091e		I pushed myself again.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	61	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_de41b086		No cough this time but I should still be more careful, there is no need to explore until I collapse.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	61	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_ec765010		It is almost noon. I should not keep Mrs Baxter waiting any longer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_191caa9e		I rested a while, I need to get some strength if I want to get through the day.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	79	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_46fa7278		After a little while, I am starting to feel better.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	87	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_b1f38da1		Perhaps I can use the remaining time productively.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	87	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_904e3238		A commotion from the entrance hall draws my attention.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	96	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_0ea69aa8		It seems the hunting party has returned.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	96	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_fb4436d7		I knock politely on the door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	115	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_e7eab8ec	psychic	Yes? Who is there?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	119	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_9fc6028b	nurse	It is Rosalind Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	123	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_ef454898	psychic	Oh, Miss Marsh, I am resting my eyes at present.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	127	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_63ed1bf9	psychic	But I'll join you for luncheon.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	127	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_8900bd06	psychic	Might we speak then?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	127	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_psychic_busy_f84ea5f4	nurse	Of course.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	135	nurse "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_48f97549		The room has a heavy, sweet scent to it. Something thick, like incense or dried lavender.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_4da47d00		A deck of unusual cards is spread across the dressing table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_a33dccbf		Several books on spiritualism and the occult are stacked carelessly by the bed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_7f0dbe18		I look through the drawers, but find only clothes and more peculiar trinkets.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_117b2d83		There is nothing of real value here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_5f2120c2		I am about to leave when I hear footsteps in the corridor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_e7002357		The door opens.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_2110df15	psychic	Oh —	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	169	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_de87ddce		Mrs Baxter stops in the doorway. Her eyes move slowly across the room, then settle on me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	173	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_c1dd46d2	nurse	Mrs Baxter. Forgive me — I have made a dreadful mistake. I thought this was my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	177	nurse "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_fe80b18b		A brief silence. I hold her gaze steadily.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	181	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_835baa34	psychic	Your room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	185	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_be57b981	nurse	The corridor all looks rather alike at this end. I am sorry to have disturbed you. I shall leave you to rest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	189	nurse "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_fb222dd4	psychic	Yes. I came back to lie down for a short while.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	193	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_259ce5b7		She does not move from the doorway. Her expression is difficult to read — polite enough on the surface, but there is something watchful underneath.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	197	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_7dca46b1	psychic	It is curious, though.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	201	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_182a6112	psychic	I am quite certain I locked the door when I left this morning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	201	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_585adaa5		She says it lightly, almost to herself. But her gaze does not leave me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_d7236aba	nurse	Perhaps the latch did not catch properly. These old doors can be unreliable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	211	nurse "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_725005ad	psychic	Perhaps.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	215	psychic "[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_d633f512		I step past her into the corridor, keeping my pace unhurried.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	219	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_96b3f8d9		She watches me go.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	219	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_089e516f		She is not a fool.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	219	"[what]"
nurse_search_psychic_caught_fdc828c5		Whatever she thinks now, she will be watching me more carefully from this moment on.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	219	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_cancel_b19106ca		I have no desire to wander further for the time being.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day2_no_hunt_cancel_c16a32b7		I shall stay in my room and rest until the others return.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_79af890c		Amelia Baxter comes a bit later.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	9	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_f336d0b8		She is composed as ever when she arrives.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	9	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_3d0b1e89		She takes the chair across from me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	9	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_e34c0aa5		Mrs Baxter is already seated when I arrive, composed as ever.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	19	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_68018f42		I take the chair across from her.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	19	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_032911b0	psychic	Miss Marsh, how are you?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	25	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_56650b33	nurse	Fine, thank you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	29	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_c78b71e5	psychic	It seems we have not yet had a proper chance to talk, have we?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	33	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_21b61c75	nurse	Indeed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	37	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_65265d9a		A member of the household staff steps in quietly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	43	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_e38fe3a1	maid	Excuse me for interrupting, but do you ladies need some lunch?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	47	maid "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_6013b815	nurse	That would be lovely, thank you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	51	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_51809372		She returns shortly with some plates.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_fe60e804		We eat and exchange pleasantries.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_a5d86917		When we have finished, I set my napkin aside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	65	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_8c3b15df		I have been feeling out of sorts all morning, and the feeling has not quite left me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	65	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_9b7448f7		A cough escapes me, sharper than I expected.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	73	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_4ad0df88	nurse	I am feeling rather poorly, I am afraid.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	77	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_93a3756f	nurse	I think I shall retire to my room for a short while.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	77	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_ea4c3888	nurse	Would you mind being left on your own?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	77	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_eb4738c3	psychic	Not at all, please don't concern yourself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	85	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_327f8a5d	psychic	There is more than enough here to occupy me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	85	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_ae0506ea		I leave her to it and make my way back upstairs.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	91	"[what]"
nurse_day2_hunt_tea_room_468d8123		A brief rest should do me good before the hunting party returns.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	91	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_downstairs_maid_d3d9d577		I ease the door open just enough to look inside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	64	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_downstairs_maid_bf83e33b		The kitchen is a hive of activity.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	64	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_downstairs_maid_bf4dc664		The staff are busy cleaning after the evening meal.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	64	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_downstairs_maid_0a07a80d		I withdraw before anyone notices my presence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	64	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_tea_room_15593824		The room is empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	84	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_tea_room_f62eb111		The fire has burned low.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	84	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_tea_room_f2145016		I sit for a moment but find no comfort in it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	84	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_tea_room_d5661a37		I shall try elsewhere.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	84	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dining_room_6dd52ce2		The dining room has been cleared.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	103	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dining_room_b4f8b041		Only the large table remains, bare and polished under the cold light.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	103	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dining_room_72f0dda7		There is nothing to keep me here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	103	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_garden_71a3c38b		I step towards the door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	120	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_garden_215fed2f		It is dark outside, and the wind has risen again.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	120	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_garden_ad38b980		There is nothing to be gained by wandering out there in the cold.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	120	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_garden_313e571d		I turn and go back in.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	120	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_entrance_hall_1649049d		The great hall is very quiet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_entrance_hall_31508737		The place where Doctor Baldwin was carried in is no different from any other part of the floor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_entrance_hall_7325d4ed		And yet I cannot quite look at it without thinking of him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_entrance_hall_3b7ece02		I move on.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_portrait_gallery_bf638e83		The gallery is lit only by a single lamp at the far end.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	158	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_portrait_gallery_5cd165b0		The portraits watch me in silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	158	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_3dfa53a2		I knock quietly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_cde4eaca		There is no answer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_c9f73d3f		The house is still on edge after today's events.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_cb5279bb		It is no great surprise that people are keeping their doors shut.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_eaf22562		I shall not press the matter.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_0f00efd5		Still no answer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	192	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_closed_61355713		I shall not disturb them again.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	192	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_lad_afac049a		I approach Mr Harring's room and knock gently.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_lad_eb8deb80		There is no reply, but I can hear the sound of heavy furniture being dragged across the floorboards.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_lad_6494220d		It seems he is barricading himself inside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_lad_84314d5d		Under the circumstances, I suppose I cannot blame him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_default_room_no_enter_4ccf5b09		It is best I do not go in there for now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	225	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_captain_06ad4a2b		Captain Sinha is nowhere to be seen, though I suspect he is not far away.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	235	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_captain_65e9e481		This corridor remains quite deserted as well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	241	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_captain_18f6ef1a		With most of the household downstairs or retired, one could easily slip inside unseen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_captain_9e72416c		Though it would be rather difficult to explain if I were caught.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_bfbe68b8		As I turn to leave, I notice something I had not expected.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_fd15e5ab		A heavy hunting jacket hangs on the hook by the door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_bb240f11		It does not match the rest of the room's careful order — it looks as though it was tossed there in haste.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_b2bc8d1b		The Captain must have changed for dinner and left it behind.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_again_ab6633e6		But wait — something is different.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	303	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_again_b7971142		A hunting jacket now hangs on the hook by the door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	303	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_enter_captain_again_91b9bfc8		That was not there before. The Captain must have changed for dinner since my last visit.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	303	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_host_8ca14678		It is highly unusual for Lady Claythorn to be absent from her room at this hour.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_host_65e9e481		This corridor remains quite deserted as well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	325	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_host_18f6ef1a		With most of the household downstairs or retired, one could easily slip inside unseen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	341	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_host_9e72416c		Though it would be rather difficult to explain if I were caught.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	341	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_b282f686		The door to Doctor Baldwin's room stands open.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_ff2eb8e3		I step inside, and the stillness of the room is immediate.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_059cc224		He lies on the bed, just as they left him after the tragedy.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_4e469d17		It feels wrong to be here, in the presence of a colleague who has met such a sudden end.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_e6dffa90		There is nothing a nurse can do for him now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_8d135ee8		I shall leave him to his rest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	374	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_e7eab8ec	psychic	Yes? Who is there?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	399	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_117572eb	nurse	Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	403	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_eb00f6fa	nurse	I only wished to enquire whether you were quite all right.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	403	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_2ab74847	psychic	Oh, Miss Marsh. You are very kind to ask.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	409	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_ee6873f8	psychic	But I am quite exhausted, if I am perfectly honest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	409	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_ec5ee318	psychic	I really just wish to sleep now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	409	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_f84ea5f4	nurse	Of course.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	417	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_35e73d39	nurse	I shall not keep you. We shall both feel better in the morning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	417	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_948a5ba4	psychic	Indeed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	423	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_1393ba25	psychic	Good night, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	423	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_psychic_4510c80d	nurse	Good night.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	429	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_0bbf53f8	drunk	Hmm... urrh...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	444	drunk "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_6c08bb81		He is quite beyond rational conversation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	448	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_dc4cb4ec		I step back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	448	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_4b42ca1c		There is nothing to be done for him tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	448	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_e4f0b8ec		A cough comes to me, a strong one.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	553	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_a45d4bad		I reach for my handkerchief to cover my mouth.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	553	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_d48758a9		It is followed by a second.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	561	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_418cab86		It should not come as a surprise; I haven't rested as much as I ought to.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	561	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_8ed38ce1		The only sane thing to do now is to go to bed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	561	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_check_exhaustion_89c4121d		If I don't, God knows what could happen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	561	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_46715047		I hear them before I see them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_cc4628a9		There is a commotion at the front door, a confusion of voices.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_090ab623		Then the door swings wide and the hunting party files in.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_7dfa5df7		Something is wrong.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_a9370713		Lady Claythorn's face is ashen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_2bb809c8		Two of the men are carrying someone between them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_f764dda5		I step forward at once.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_60991901		The Captain takes charge with admirable promptness.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_bdada941		I watch as Ted Harring helps carry the body up the stairs.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_210db007		I keep to one side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_0d06e423		There is nothing more for me to do for Doctor Baldwin now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_f44b8107		I watch the Captain lead Samuel Manning away.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_51a1e6b9		The man goes quietly, which surprises me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_eb781300		He seems to have only a dim sense of what has happened.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	69	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_b33f8aba		I return to my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dbfd1583		I sit on the edge of the bed and press my fingers together.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_c7b32dd3		A man is dead.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_46527d19		I have seen men die before, many of them, at far closer quarters than this.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_9090e37f		Yet there is something particular about a death in a house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_61fa6cb6		It leaves a stillness in the air that does not belong there.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	83	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_f1f4f1f1		I think of the Captain and what I found in the library.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_e40aea5e		His account of his wound at Zanzibar seemed improbable to me from the start.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_f60a03ef		After today, I am no longer sure what to make of him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_4bba40b1		He acted with authority and presence of mind.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_2bc86c99		But that, in itself, proves nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_6707996f		I decide I should rest before dinner.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_1d2f1b81		The gong sounds.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	121	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_7b2c724f		I would prefer to stay in my room, but that would raise questions.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	121	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_41b682b9		The dining room is noticeably quieter than it was last night.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_af37e315		Three chairs sit empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_7472458f		I take my usual place and look around the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_b85a9d0f		But I realise that I have no one in front of me, nor to my side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_be9cdc51		Lady Claythorn observes my awkward position.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_a2b0f1e7	host	I think it's better if you come sit next to me tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	143	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_a690d0e8	host	No reason to leave you alone at the end of the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	143	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_5dd7ece7	nurse	Thank you.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	149	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_abc23be5		Everyone is subdued.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	153	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dc856647		Lady Claythorn stands.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	153	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_4fad9862		A measured speech.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_a897bd33		She holds herself well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_539e7e63		I find myself wondering what she is actually feeling beneath that composed exterior.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_4c421836		Now that she is sitting to my right, I have the opportunity to question her.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	161	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_464d0a5e		Dinner ends.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_ecc22344		The butler sees the guests out of the room with quiet efficiency.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_5d74b2d8		Most of the others drift away towards their rooms.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_3c7e7c7a		Before they all leave, my eyes settle on the silverware scattered about the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_c940c617		It would be so easy to slide a piece into my bag undetected.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_67db93f3		The others are distracted by the evening's events.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_dbd42c27		I do not feel ready to sleep just yet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	202	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_7af75357		The manor is quiet, but that is not the same as saying it is safe.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	202	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_022cf2d9		Perhaps I ought to make a brief exploration before I retire.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	202	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_15f2006c		A cough catches me by surprise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_f5cec5a1		I stop and press a hand against the wall until it passes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_1192003a		When it does, I become suddenly aware of how late it must be.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_a8eaea07		I have been wandering this house for too long.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_1e201f5e		That was not wise of me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_041e5cbc		There are some indulgences I cannot afford, and pushing myself through the small hours of the night is one of them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_65e746bb		I shall not press my luck further tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	227	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_428107aa		I return to my room and lock the door behind me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	243	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_68dbc675		It has been a long day.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	249	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_206341d5		It is time to sleep.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	249	"[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_591dbbf9	nurse	It has been a dreadful day, has it not, Lady Claythorn?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	262	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_d125a7e8	nurse	To lose such a man as Doctor Baldwin in such a manner...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	262	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_a56ade53	host	It is indeed a tragedy.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	268	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_05bb763e	nurse	And poor Mr Manning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_76702953	nurse	One can only hope the authorities arrive soon to settle this matter.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_e9cb0db8	host	Indeed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	278	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_b56fd974	host	But please, let us not dwell on such dark matters while we eat, my dear.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	278	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_dinner_host_f84ea5f4	nurse	Of course.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	284	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_bfd2a410		A cough takes me without warning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	299	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_536f05ed		Harder than the ones before.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	299	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_dada07ca		I press my handkerchief to my lips.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	299	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_d530a8ee		A second.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_e978c399		My knees feel uncertain beneath me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_14bc9033		I find the wall and lean against it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_fc5d61c8		A third, and I cannot check it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_d2850640		I sink down.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_bfa1a299		The handkerchief, when I pull it away, tells me everything I already knew.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_1e0e8fa9		The floor is very cold.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_exhaution_7df769bd		I cannot seem to rise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_b5a78b15		A quick glance to either side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_a13f2d41		The others are moving towards the door, their backs turned.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_30c4fc9f		My hand moves, sliding a silver spoon into my bag with the faintest clink.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	336	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_4cef7a75		Nobody seems to notice.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	350	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_do_not_steal_e7d64e02		I look at the silverware for a moment longer than I ought.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	359	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_do_not_steal_56c887cd		Then I push the thought aside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	359	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_do_not_steal_23701cc3		It is not worth the risk.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/1_main.rpy	359	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_1732ffaa		A single lamp burns at the far end of the room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_52d442f9		Captain Sinha is alone on a chair, reading.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_90ee486f		He turns as I enter, but does not seem surprised to see me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	10	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_83f8a52b		The Captain is still here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	26	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_dbcf85dc		He glances up as I enter and raises his glass slightly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	26	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_bar_0ae2dbe6		I take a step towards the sideboard, then stop myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	43	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_bar_9d3826e3		What am I doing?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	43	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_bar_67a0a455		No. That is the last thing I need tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	43	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_bar_9dd15216		I turn away before the Captain notices.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	43	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_12b886b1	captain	Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_df604cf3	captain	I thought everyone had retired.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	62	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_70bb20ea	nurse	Not quite yet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	68	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_169dfd43	nurse	There are a few things about this weekend that don't make sense to me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	68	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_647c12ab	captain	Oh?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	74	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_intro_678cd57b	captain	Such as?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	74	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_98b88c7b	nurse	Two actors employed as servants. Three of us at the same war.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	130	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_0f6eb3e5	nurse	There are too many things wrong in this house, Captain.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	130	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_7bca334e		He pauses and ponders for a second.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	136	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_5903b44b	captain	I confess it is difficult to dismiss entirely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_bab0b096	captain	And yet, taken separately, each element has a reasonable explanation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_4455acfd	captain	Actors find their way into service when times are lean.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_17009c66	captain	Three of us crossing paths in a war is not so remarkable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_b147abf2	captain	Especially since I believe most of us were invited for something related to our role in a conflict.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_83ed468a	captain	And two deaths, both apparently accidental...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	140	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_2a5c975a		He trails off. Stares into his glass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	154	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_ff140750		Then he sets it down deliberately.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	154	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_845f31db	captain	No.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	160	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_7432dd78	captain	I am inclined to agree.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	160	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_f6c3245d	captain	The sum of it is harder to explain away.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	160	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_5db84d96	captain	There is a real possibility that this weekend is not what it appears to be.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	160	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_127574ce	nurse	That's what I believe too.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	170	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_6f45860d	captain	But how to be sure?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	174	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_a15a5127	captain	There is still a chance that all of this is a coincidence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	174	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_35c50828	captain	I don't want to put Lady Claythorn in an awkward position if she has done nothing wrong.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	174	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_0c968c62	captain	That would be improper.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	174	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_4472791b		He won't mention it, but he is certainly not just worried about making a scandal.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	184	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_02537883		He is thinking about the reward as well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	184	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_8a5bd860		Antagonising Lady Claythorn could make her renounce giving the prize.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	184	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_2683c1d3		That's a powerful incentive to keep people in line.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	184	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_34c63e01		But I cannot just do nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	184	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_676e031f	nurse	There is someone else we can question.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	196	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_2d8f6fcb	nurse	The only other person on staff I have seen this weekend.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	196	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_8fda46ae	captain	You mean the butler?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	202	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_4ebf90b1	nurse	Precisely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	206	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_0bb7e2de	captain	That's not a bad idea.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	210	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_c8684457	captain	If we could find that he too is not a career servant, that would confirm our suspicions, and we could confront Lady Claythorn about it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	210	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_285c0b88	captain	But we cannot simply march up to the man and demand an explanation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	210	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_ecff943a	captain	If there is something amiss, he is not going to confess over a polite enquiry.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	210	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_63b794ad	nurse	Then perhaps we should try a less polite one.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	220	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_9cf38366		He looks at me sharply.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	224	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_a0b3a5c2	captain	You mean threaten him?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_299b7010	captain	That would be unwise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_c20f63e1	captain	And more than a little dangerous.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_7899f0da	captain	Besides, if you want to make a man talk, you would need to properly frighten him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_71e555e9	captain	And I do not have anything that would do the trick.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_3a0f04bb	captain	At least not here with me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_1d8279ac	captain	So it's better not to think of it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	228	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_9afdc04a	nurse	What would you need?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	244	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_1973e717	captain	Well, I don't like talking about those things with a lady.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_53b009f9	captain	But if you must know, a gun can get a confession from almost any man.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_7804acb5	captain	I mean at least if it is loaded, that way you can show that you are serious about the matter.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_1d0bf209	captain	I have seen battle-hardened soldiers lose all confidence when a gun is shot close to them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_445bfbca	captain	But I don't have one with me here, so I don't think I can do anything.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_5c1363ff	captain	I am afraid we must just be on our guard tonight, and leave as soon as possible in the morning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_a10b51ba	captain	Yes, now that I think of it, that's the only sensible thing to do.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	248	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_9758c2d3		He turns back to his book, for him the conversation is over.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	264	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_eb0a75fa		I don't like this but I won't convince him with words only.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	264	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_4915cf68	nurse	Exactly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_d0c931bb	nurse	That is proof that something is very wrong here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_bbcd4213	captain	I wouldn't say proof, not yet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	278	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_suspicions_f1bd2c42	captain	You will need more than that to convince me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	278	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_0c5b22e3	nurse	I believe that something strange is going on with the staff.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	289	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_9492924a	captain	In what sense?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	293	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_e6bb2a8e		I should be careful here. I cannot say I went searching their rooms.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	297	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_e27fd0bf	nurse	The maid.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	301	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_9b8c8524	nurse	I have seen her before. Not here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	301	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_e1f817db	nurse	In London, at the theatre, playing a role.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	301	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_39195dad	nurse	I can't quite remember the name of the play, but I am certain that it is her.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	301	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_02f5721a	captain	You think you saw a housemaid on stage.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	311	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_5bcb7bd6	nurse	I do not think it. I know it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	315	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_3ceb387e	nurse	And that is not all.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	315	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_e3a5eb37	nurse	The footman. I have seen him in a play as well.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	315	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_38885431	nurse	A different production, but I am quite sure of it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	315	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_aeaa1fb2	captain	You attend a great deal of theatre, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	325	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_8d890728	nurse	I do, as it happens.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	329	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_e1e57bea	nurse	And I know what I saw.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	329	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_8d67a5d1	nurse	Two actors, both employed as servants in the same country house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	329	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_d93b2be1	nurse	That cannot be a coincidence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	329	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_b8ef39c3		He is quiet for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	339	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_1b4e0aeb		Then, to my surprise, he does not dismiss it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	339	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_bcdd8e92	captain	It is indeed hard to believe.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	345	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_efa89e15	captain	In London that would perhaps be possible.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	345	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_staff_3ebe5ad8	captain	But here, very unlikely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	345	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_7e585b24	nurse	Yesterday you told a story about the Boxer Rebellion.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	362	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_6bd2a90d	captain	Yes, I might have. What of it?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	366	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_0047cf26	nurse	I was there too, you know.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	370	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_610e27dd	nurse	As a nurse, attached to the field hospital.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	370	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_25e1e0a5		He pauses.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	376	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_984f4887		This surprises him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	376	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_a6f07d9a	captain	Were you indeed?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	382	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_0cd0c2a1	captain	That is a remarkable coincidence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	382	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_f784d275	nurse	There is more.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	388	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_7d29c06f	nurse	Daniel Baldwin was there too.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	388	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_3752414a	nurse	He was a young doctor at the time — I am almost certain of it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	388	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_2a09be49	nurse	When you spoke of your campaign on Friday evening, it all came back to me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	388	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_b8ef39c3		He is quiet for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	398	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_e62e1305	captain	Baldwin.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	402	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_cf3e4957	captain	Yes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	402	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_5193967d	captain	I might remember a doctor by that name.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	402	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_ba1e9d67	captain	But I never made the connection. It is not as though we were in the same circles.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	402	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_1035c2ac	captain	This is very strange.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	402	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_af43571a		He is quiet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	414	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_b2d0cd56		The fire crackles between us.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	414	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_2c7c006d	nurse	I thought so too, at first.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	420	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_5bd88470	nurse	A coincidence. Three people who happened to be in the same country at the same time, twenty-four years ago.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	420	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_619de6af	nurse	But then the doctor died.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	420	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_cb1e84e8	captain	You are saying his death changes things.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	428	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_c478fd15	nurse	I am saying I cannot stop thinking about it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	432	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_93947e1c	nurse	If there is something behind it — if the connection means something — then the question becomes: are we the only ones?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	432	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_d880ce28	captain	You think there may be others here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	438	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_301e81bd	nurse	I have been wondering if anyone else here might have been present.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	442	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_8a67c496	nurse	Thomas Moody, perhaps?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	442	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_41884f49	captain	Moody.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	448	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_f372e6ec	captain	It is not impossible, I suppose.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	448	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_ce7aec57	captain	Though I could not say with any certainty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	448	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_b8fe7a2b	captain	It would be difficult to recognise him with his mask on.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	448	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_ccd4745c	nurse	What about Ted Harring?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	458	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_845f31db	captain	No.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	462	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_877acdbe	captain	Far too young.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	462	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_40ac5635	captain	He would have been a boy.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	462	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_2d3696a3	nurse	Lady Claythorn? Samuel Manning? Mrs Baxter?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	470	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_b0816bb1	captain	I honestly do not remember.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	474	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_f24f83fa	captain	It was a long time ago, and there were a great many people passing through those camps.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	474	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_08a5a8a1	captain	I would not stake much on absence of memory.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	474	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_6c3baffc		He sets down his glass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	482	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_abd57f4a	captain	Three guests at this table who were all in China at the same time.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	486	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_boxer_fd77aafa	captain	It is strange, I grant you that.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	486	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_93a4282a	nurse	Captain, I have heard you talk a great deal about your campaigns.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	501	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_60004db0	nurse	And there are details that trouble me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	501	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_f49e84a7	captain	Really, which details?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	507	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_75d2443a	nurse	Well first, I can tell you with some confidence that Indian officers did not hold the rank of captain at the time of the Boxer Rebellion.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	511	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_b4ba8259	nurse	Not then. And it still must be very rare today.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	511	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_b4537bc9		A stillness settles over him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	517	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_55476744	captain	You are not wrong.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_9e22aeee	captain	I was not officially a captain.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_00eff036	captain	I was a Subedar. The highest rank allowed for a non-white officer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_ea82e0c6	captain	The law at the time made quite sure that — no matter one's ability — a coloured man could never give orders to a white man.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_890fe365	captain	But explaining all that in polite company is tedious, and tends to sour the mood, which is why I omitted it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_edd1d754	captain	But the rest of my account is true.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	521	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_36d7d127	nurse	Is it?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	535	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_76f2da4f	nurse	Because I have also looked into the Anglo-Zanzibar War.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	535	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_b558b7a3	nurse	The entire engagement lasted less than an hour. British naval artillery. No real resistance to speak of.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	535	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_680f97df	nurse	The fighting you described does not quite correspond to the historical record.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	535	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_483ef56e		He does not flinch.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	545	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_46d45ff4		If anything, he straightens slightly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	545	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_1581a0e9	captain	I was there, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	551	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_8db403ab	captain	And I was wounded.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	551	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_27927189	nurse	Wounded.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	557	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_46792044	nurse	In an engagement that lasted forty-five minutes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	557	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_16c88f6e	nurse	With only one man lightly injured on the British side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	557	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_b8ef39c3		He is quiet for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	565	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_7fc8d199		Then he sets down his glass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	565	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_0e0ae817	captain	Well, my injuries were perhaps so minor that they were not reported.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	571	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_34ea16a0	captain	War is a messy business. Not everything that happened can be recorded in history books.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	571	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_4e66abc5	captain	But I must admit I might have been carried away with my description.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	571	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_bbf21a02	captain	You see, a good story does not simply recount the facts.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	571	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_d4ba336d	captain	Perhaps I lent mine a little colour. That is not the same as dishonesty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	571	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_994b12eb		He smiles.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	583	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_war_stories_a89d62ff		It is true that he could just have exaggerated some facts, but I am not entirely convinced.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	583	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_a2338169		I reach into my coat and produce the revolver I got from the gun room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	596	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_83338452		Captain Sinha looks at me astonished.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	596	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_d1cb89c3	captain	Miss Marsh, how on earth do you have this with you?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	602	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_9c45ca5a		Again, it's probably best to not tell the truth.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	606	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5e7a1501	nurse	I learnt during the war that it is better to always be prepared.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	611	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_513a763e	nurse	I have never left my house without it since.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	611	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_d9762719		I hope this lie is convincing enough.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	617	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_22b30a3e	nurse	It is loaded.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	621	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_3d91d6c6	nurse	Two people are dead, Captain. The staff are impostors. Three of us were at the very same war twenty-four years ago.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	621	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_6c5cb4ab	nurse	Something is very wrong in this house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	621	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5340c9bb	nurse	You are a military man.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	621	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_01f95ab8	nurse	Take the gun, and let's confront the butler.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	621	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_6828d41f		I hold it out to him.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_e3fb023d		He does not move.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_b5497988		The silence stretches between us, broken only by the crackle of the fire.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_4510911c		Then I see it — something I have not seen in him before.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5b4d048d		Not caution. Not calculation.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5b139dd4		Fear.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	633	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_12b886b1	captain	Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	649	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_9fe00262	captain	I...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	649	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_c7f7ae93		He stops. Starts again.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	655	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_2f9fe63e	captain	I cannot take that gun.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	659	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_26fcebe5	nurse	Why not?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	663	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_6cc60c45		He looks at me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	669	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_9b37c8da		And the mask he has worn all weekend — the upright soldier, the man of experience, the captain — slips, just slightly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	669	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_381dc4ff	captain	I have held a rifle on a hunt, yes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	675	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_395ce0c7	captain	I have shot at birds and game.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	675	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_c6df00fc	captain	But I have never once pointed a weapon at another human being.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	675	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5069ff61	captain	Not in China. Not in Zanzibar. Not anywhere.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	675	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_8f71e87f		The words come slowly, as though each one costs him something.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	685	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_20174c99	captain	I was never on the front lines, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	689	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_202fd9e6	captain	I was behind them. Always safe in an office far from the action.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	689	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_9f6098b0	captain	The battles I describe — I watched some of them from a distance.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	689	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_c19204da	captain	Others I only read about in reports.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	689	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_b9ffbbcc	nurse	Then everything you told us —	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	699	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_3910c530	captain	Were stories.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	703	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_00ea427b	captain	Very old stories, told so many times it nearly became the truth in my mind.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	703	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_296d1896		He presses his hands together and stares at the fire.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	709	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_07bbed08	captain	I cannot walk into that room with a loaded revolver and threaten a man.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_e0038a5e	captain	I would not know how.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_ccc3965b	captain	I could perhaps use a gun in self-defence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_4dc8607d	captain	But not in cold blood. Not like this.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_d6d8f6cc	captain	If it came to it, I don't know that I could pull the trigger.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_35fbcfb3	captain	I have never had to.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	713	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_894bcfde	nurse	I see.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	729	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_9d4b3261	nurse	Then you are a fraud.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	729	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_23630829	nurse	Every word. Every story. Every medal you claim to have earned.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	729	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_53cb8e6d	nurse	All of it, a lie.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	729	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_a31afc76	captain	Miss Marsh, please —	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	739	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_ea78610e	nurse	No, you don't understand. You have to take the gun. Our lives depend on it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	743	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_91d3d5a8	nurse	And if you don't, then...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	743	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_cbb94dc6	nurse	Then I shall make sure everyone in here knows exactly what sort of man you are.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	743	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_99467e9e		Something changes in his expression.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	751	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_4c32e467	captain	You would not dare.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	755	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_67071027	nurse	Why not? After all, if you are an impostor, that makes you suspicious.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	759	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_11174d0d	nurse	Everyone deserves to know it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	759	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_05e9fb15		He rises from the chair.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	765	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_7775f815		I do not step back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	765	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_dd86c0cc	captain	You don't understand. If the word goes out, I'll be finished.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	771	captain angry "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5c958764	captain	My standing in London reduced to nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	771	captain angry "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_c7b25ac0	captain	You can't say anything.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	771	captain angry "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_366d8b45		He grabs me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	779	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_970b602a		His eyes are different, like those of a madman.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	779	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_d960abcb	nurse	Captain, stop!	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	785	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_f9e955a6		He is shaking me, and I cannot get out of his grip.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	789	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_fc754795		A cough comes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	795	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_7f02fbb2		It comes the way it always comes when I have pushed too far — sudden, total, unstoppable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	795	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_35e4a248		I feel instantly that it is stronger than other times.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	795	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_76e022c9		Blood splatters on Captain Sinha, who lets me go and jumps back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	795	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_7f2ccf78		My legs are weak.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	795	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_2ad5cc62		I slip to the floor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	809	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_f7564698		I keep hearing the Captain's voice, but it's is getting softer and softer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	809	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_confront_5ebbffbc		Until I cannot make out the words.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	809	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_a28b6d65	nurse	We've witnessed two deaths in as many days.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	824	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_e1b3d8c6	nurse	Doesn't it seem strange to you?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	824	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_a394ff51	captain	Not really.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	830	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_d26ea021	captain	They seem quite natural to me, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	830	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_24b913ae	captain	Thomas Moody died of injuries he got during the war.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	830	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_64561984	captain	Even if you thought he was fine, he might have been suffering in silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	830	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_dd5d55f6	captain	Some people prefer to hide their distress from the people around them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	830	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_8a555dcb		He looks at me intently as he is saying those words.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	842	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_cb395b0d		Could it be that he found out about my condition?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	842	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_70a42952	nurse	But for Doctor Baldwin?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	848	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_cdf7b636	captain	A dreadful accident, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	852	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_ae949b2a	captain	Manning was drunk and careless with a firearm.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	852	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_8a109f22	captain	Sadly, this type of tragic event is not rare at all.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	852	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_5aeb9b2e	captain	Although some people treat it as a light form of entertainment, a hunt is a dangerous business.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	852	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_cea142f7	nurse	Perhaps you are right.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	862	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_0d6127ac	nurse	Still, I confess I am uneasy knowing Samuel Manning is just upstairs.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	862	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_39955671	nurse	A few steps from my own room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	862	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_f0ec5231	nurse	Are we sure he cannot get out?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	862	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_ed3d35a9	captain	Quite sure.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	872	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_bada6c51	captain	I locked the door myself, with the key the butler gave me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	872	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_3c842907	captain	The doors in this house are solid oak. He is going nowhere.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	872	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_e9d812a9	nurse	That is reassuring.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	880	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_manning_1488a7d3		Especially since I am now in possession of that key.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	886	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_47e35c34	nurse	Do you still have the butler's key with you?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	895	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_4448dbb1		He sets down his glass and regards me steadily.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	899	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_d6b262e9	captain	Why do you ask?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	903	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_37e4fad9	nurse	Just to reassure myself.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	907	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_e9ccc3a9	nurse	I won't be able to sleep if I am not absolutely sure that Samuel Manning is properly locked in his room, with no way of escaping.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	907	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_8b650c3d		He holds my gaze for a moment, then seems to decide the question is reasonable enough.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	913	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_2130b4d1	captain	Of course.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	917	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_4a52068b	captain	It is still right here with me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	917	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_785e4ec0		He reaches into his jacket pocket.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	923	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_526cdfb3		Then stops.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	923	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_6058876a		His hand comes out empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	923	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_24eab389	captain	Blast.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	931	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_b694006c	captain	I had it earlier, but it is in my hunting coat.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	931	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_0ca5a4c1	captain	Upstairs, in my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	931	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_8be5547d	captain	I changed for dinner and left it in the pocket.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	931	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_894bcfde	nurse	I see.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	941	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_7efcfde8	captain	You shouldn't worry, I still locked my room with my regular key.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	945	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_58a52f35	captain	It is safe there.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	945	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_captain_key_d9d213c6	nurse	Good.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	951	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_leave_13e3f175		I have nothing more to say tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	960	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_leave_708fda2b	captain	Good night, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	964	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_billiard_room_leave_4510c80d	nurse	Good night.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_billiard_room.rpy	968	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_df1158d0	butler	Forgive me, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	5	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_b6f802ed	butler	I believe that item belongs with the service.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	5	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_0f77cfd7		I freeze.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	11	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ba92f752		The butler is standing entirely too close, his expression as impassive as ever.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	11	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a62fe1fe		He extends an open, expectant hand.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	11	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_9d00f556	nurse	I can explain.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	19	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_c4290df9	nurse	I assure you, it is a misunderstanding.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	19	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2c70bbbf	host	Is there a problem?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	25	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_05afc811		Lady Claythorn pauses at the doorway, her sharp eyes taking in the scene.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2f7d4ef6	butler	I observed Miss Marsh securing a piece of the silverware in her bag, my lady.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	33	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_aac66979	host	Is this true?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	37	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2dfb617b		Every excuse I have ever rehearsed vanishes at once.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	41	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_86e4c1ee		My throat tightens. My hands will not stop trembling.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	41	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_cb1454ee		No point in denying now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	41	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_95fa95d9		I slowly reach inside my bag and place the silver spoon back upon the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	41	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_c04be5a7	host	Miss Marsh, I can hardly believe it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	51	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6e160bea	nurse	Lady Claythorn, please...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	55	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_51c96444	nurse	I had no intention of keeping it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	55	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_9c3baf6f	nurse	I was only admiring the craftsmanship.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	55	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_569591d4		Lady Claythorn looks straight at me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	63	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_fd6a1810		A hard look that says she does not believe me, not a single word.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	63	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_95cdab58		But that she also does not quite know what to do.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	63	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_12923a99	nurse	Please, believe me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	71	nurse scared "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4d7276fc	nurse	This is all a terrible misunderstanding!	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	71	nurse scared "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_dc6cebe5	butler	Forgive me, my lady, but I am not in the habit of making mistakes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	77	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4aa00df2	butler	I noted several pieces missing after luncheon.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	77	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_318164db	butler	That is why I took it upon myself to be more watchful this evening.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	77	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_b41db2ea		This silences everyone in the room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	85	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8548becf		All eyes are fixed upon me now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	85	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_b20b45ad	captain	Several pieces, you say?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	91	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_9894058e	captain	Then we ought to know exactly how far this has gone.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	91	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2c3d1dfe		The Captain turns to the butler without waiting for Lady Claythorn's leave.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	97	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_7d2d2539	captain	Go to Miss Marsh's room and search her belongings.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	101	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2a582952	captain	If she has taken anything else, bring it here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	101	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4348d46d	butler	At once, sir.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	107	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_02bf1f4d		He leaves without another word.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_1423f171		I stand rooted to the spot, my heart hammering against my ribs.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_008ef44f		No one speaks. Lady Claythorn remains in the doorway, watching me with that terrible, steady gaze.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8975042d		The Captain stands with his arms folded. The others avoid my eyes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_0dff97a1		The minutes stretch unbearably.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	111	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_35a3d971	nurse	Please, this really is not necessary...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	123	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_fbcf63d2	captain	I rather think it is.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	127	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_70b54edf		At last, I hear footsteps on the stairs.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_680e7401		The butler reappears, carrying a small cloth bundle which he sets upon the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_5e5b50de		He unfolds it carefully, revealing a silver spoon and a fork, identical to the ones we have been using this weekend.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	131	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_1605aaba	butler	These were in Miss Marsh's travelling case, my lady.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	139	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8b438ba6	butler	Concealed beneath her garments.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	139	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6c86922a		He reaches into the cloth once more and produces a string of pearls, which he sets down beside the cutlery.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_0529f95f	butler	And these, my lady.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	151	butler "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_1f553a2a	host	My pearls!	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	155	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d90c704e	host	Good heavens, those are my pearls!	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	155	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a56cf3e3	host	I was planning to wear them this very evening!	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	155	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_9518d649		Lady Claythorn's composure cracks, if only for a moment, before she steadies herself again.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	163	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_61703dc2		The room falls utterly silent.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	167	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a468e096		There is nothing left to say. The evidence is laid out before them, plain as day.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	167	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_bc09d5b8	captain	Given what has just been found, I think we can dispense with any further talk of misunderstandings.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_36ba566d	captain	Miss Marsh is clearly not who she claims to be.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	173	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d6c80ed0		I try to think of an answer, but words elude me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	179	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2cf6076a	lad	What are we going to do then?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	184	lad "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_c1ce9c5b	psychic	We cannot possibly allow her to roam the house freely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	188	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6b9f82f5	psychic	I am sorry, Miss Marsh, but I shall not feel safe until you are secured somewhere.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	188	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8c735d52	captain	We ought to confine her to her room, just as we did with Mr Manning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	194	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d76cacc9	captain	Tomorrow, we shall let the police sort this out.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	194	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4a491a30	captain	Allow me to escort her upstairs, Lady Claythorn.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	194	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_bad3ebd6	host	Yes, I think that is wise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	202	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d43a7db7	host	Thank you, Captain.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	202	host "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_c9348821		I try to muster some dignity, but with all their eyes upon me, there is none to be found.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ab8e5495		I follow the Captain upstairs with my head bowed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_96b8db4e		He walks closely behind me the whole way, ensuring I do not stray.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_1b203ece		When I reach my room, I step inside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	218	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6159a64e		The door closes firmly behind me, followed by the definitive click of a key turning in the lock.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	218	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_e6d16ce8	captain	Forgive me, Miss Marsh. I have no choice in the matter.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	224	captain "[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_50b8723b		His footsteps retreat down the corridor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_90f0db06		I press my back against the door and sink to the floor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6a340901		I don't think the police will arrest me for this.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_2c88e9c1		But what will happen if the words go out?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_21392e6d		My reputation could be gone in an instant.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6e55a8da		I sit there for a long while, staring at nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	228	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_0730c692		Then something steadies inside me. Self-pity will not help me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_df073bc1		They believe I am trapped here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_9c8893ee		But a hairpin and a steady hand are all I require to open my door.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_516c0a64		I shall wait until the house is completely silent, and then I will take my leave.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_96acc893		Certainly, they will not come after me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_e7282120		Not for such a minor small crime.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6af8366c		I could leave and it would be as I've never been here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	248	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d53ccdc5		I slip out into the hallway undetected.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	268	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d4055878		Nobody is there.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	268	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a2e7d2a6		I keep close to the walls, hoping I do not run into any servants performing their night duties.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	268	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_e00ac055		But the manor is dead silent.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	268	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_46d33cda		I reach the entrance hall and look one last time upon the impressive place.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	280	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8a2034d3		I force the lock, then quickly make my way outside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	280	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_7726cb5b		The night air hits me like a slap.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_df4f169f		I keep to the shadows, moving along the side of the house towards the drive.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_bbac2ef4		Then I stop.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4c367568		Ahead, near the garage, a motorcar stands with its engine running, its headlamps cutting two pale beams into the dark.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a5db0b5a		Figures are moving around it — quickly, purposefully.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_744ab547		I press myself flat against the wall and watch.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	288	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ae3edd2c		The butler emerges first, carrying two heavy cases which he loads into the boot.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	302	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_7f5f9b12		Behind him, the footman and the maid, each with bags of their own.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	302	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_13f007f3		And then Lady Claythorn herself, wrapped in a fur coat, clutching a leather valise to her chest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	302	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ad846e7f		She does not look back at the house. Not once.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	302	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_de464689		She climbs into the rear of the motorcar without a word.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	302	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_30669dca		The doors close. The engine growls.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	314	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_53642ae1		The motorcar pulls away down the drive, its lights shrinking into the darkness until they are gone entirely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	314	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_17daff6a		I stand there for a long moment, pressed against the cold stone, trying to make sense of what I have just seen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	314	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6b330f7c		The lady of the house, fleeing her own estate in the dead of night, with every last member of her staff.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	314	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8faeec78		Whatever is happening in this place, it's better if I don't linger.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	314	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4224874a		The road ahead is long, and the air is bitterly cold.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_e26c5921		I walk quickly at first, putting as much distance as I can between myself and the house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ee3f4cb1		But the road is dark, and I did not think to bring a lamp.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_8d5bcf34		The drive gives way to a narrow lane, then to a fork I do not remember from the journey here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_6a76e416		I choose left. Or perhaps right. I am no longer sure.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_26ea4e44		The trees press closer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	342	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_d5e7a88c		The road, if it is still a road, narrows to little more than a track.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	342	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_11d569a8		I stumble over a root and catch myself against a trunk, bark scraping my palms.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	342	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_87a6bac6		I should turn back. But turn back to where?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	342	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_36d15e90		I have lost the road entirely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	342	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_02aab1d9		The cold settles into me like water filling a glass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	354	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_b00bd901		I keep walking, but my steps grow shorter, slower.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	354	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_b6bf0cb2		The trees all look the same.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	354	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_698cd4a8		Every direction is darkness.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	354	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_3180f1f4		I sit down against a tree, just for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	364	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_4f48daa2		Just to gather my strength.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	364	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_ae2bb06a		The ground is damp and freezing, but my legs will not carry me any further.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	364	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_04fac4fc		I pull my coat tighter and close my eyes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	364	"[what]"
nurse_day2_evening_steal_caught_a93fefa2		Just for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 2/3_Evening/2_steal_caught.rpy	364	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_60101743		I wake already spent.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_ebb2dce6		A cough finds me before I am properly conscious, which is its usual way.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_4e222273		I press the handkerchief to my lips and wait for it to pass.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_bf0ceb6c		More blood this morning.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_6078844a		I fold the cloth away and sit on the edge of the bed until my head clears.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_fef5a7a0		I have been pushing myself too hard.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_0f5971f7		Hopefully, I can still hold on until the end of the day.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	35	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_6868285a		I wake to silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_1f0ab73e		Not the ordinary silence of a sleeping house — something stiller than that.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_bf8d2ca8		I lie for a moment, listening.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_77228d54		Nothing moves below.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_deca176b		I sit up.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	53	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_c14521ff		I wash and dress methodically.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	65	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_000a88d5		Whatever this morning holds, it is better faced upright and properly buttoned.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	65	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_544adb69		I make my way downstairs for breakfast.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	65	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_777707ce		The dining room is empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_1d39431f		Not merely quiet — empty in a way that stops me in the doorway.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_c6a7f21b		The grates are cold. No breakfast has been laid. The table stands exactly as it was left after last night's dinner.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_17efb680		Not a maid, not a footman. Not a sound from the kitchen.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_c299043f		I walk to the window and look out at the grounds.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_6338e68f		Nobody there either.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_7dfa5df7		Something is wrong.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_a2d97cd8		And perhaps I have known it, in some quieter part of my mind, since the moment I read that letter on the train.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_c1dede43		There is no prize here. There never was.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_47706fc3		Whatever this weekend is truly about, it has moved well beyond the point of pretending otherwise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_8d9a43cc		I should have acted sooner.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_1403ca63		I may be running out of time.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	77	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_f28a9ee8		I cross to the entrance hall and look about.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_7b76763b		No one.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_b98ad8bb		I stand in the middle of the room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_25683e75		Then something catches my eye.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_fe3c79d6		On the small side table beside the front door, placed neatly, is a key on a plain chain.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_644cae76		I pick it up.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_b8ca5b2d		It is small and well-worn, with the heft of something often used.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	105	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_f45a1253		Another master key.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_ec2acb31		I already hold one. I have no need for a second.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_804a106b		Though I wonder why this one was left here so openly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_9e953847		I set it back down.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	123	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_4b153caf		A master key, by the look of it — the kind a head of household staff would carry.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_c0637301		The sort that opens every door in the house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	139	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_2c060850		I slip the key into my coat pocket.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	147	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_212e5476		Above me, floorboards creak.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_a57421cf		I go still.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_3a1f5925		Then another creak, further along the upper corridor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_591b41d3		Someone is up, and moving.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_fc6e7762		And they will be coming downstairs before long.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_67f84d7c		I cannot afford to be found standing here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_a12ce07f		Every moment I remain is a risk.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	151	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_41259bea		I have already taken what I came for.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_a49918c4		The silver is in my bag, along with everything else I gathered this weekend.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_4d83cf2b		There is nothing left to stay for.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	169	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_22b48417		I am not sure what to do now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	189	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_285ca1e9		Two days in this house, and I have precious little to show for it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	189	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_631d892d		It's too risky to scour the entire place.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	189	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_72778220		So, if I am to leave with anything worth the trouble, I need to be clever about where I look.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	189	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_a92e23de		My mind goes to the butler's room — that reinforced cabinet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	201	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_887096ce		I know that a butler sometimes keeps a household's valuables in his quarters.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	207	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_butler_room_hint_c6b42705		It might be worth a visit before the morning is through.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	211	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_02f1e61c		An irrational feeling overtakes me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	220	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_4b5e2f27		I know I should prepare more before attempting the long journey back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	220	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_529af058		But a deep-rooted fear prevents me from getting to my room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	220	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_2d23cf0b		No. I need to leave now — there is no time to waste.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	220	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_36d18004		At least I have the valuables I acquired with me in my bag.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	232	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_d059a2d3		I take my coat from the stand.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	236	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_fdda77fd		I open the front door and step outside.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	236	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_c94c0cb9		The air is cold and sharp, but I scarcely feel it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	244	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_9b922e9d		My bag is heavy on my shoulder — heavier than it has any right to be.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	250	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_04a25a10		I walk quickly down the drive, my heels crunching on the gravel.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	254	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_a4e3ef92		I do not look back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	254	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_cf09b8de		There will be no prize. There was never going to be one.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	254	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_afceac72		I have understood that for some time now, and yet I stayed.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	254	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_3c35f565		The gate at the end of the drive. Eyes on that, and nothing else.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	254	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_24843f2f		The road stretches ahead, and the bag grows heavier with every step.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	273	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_79aa6e40		I should drop some of the silver. I know that. But I cannot bring myself to part with it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	273	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_557c384f		My legs falter beneath the weight — of the bag, of the illness, of everything I have put my body through.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	273	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_d6998059		The road stretches ahead, quiet and grey beneath the morning cloud.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_834331c9		I keep walking — or I try to.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_28940838		My legs feel heavier with every step.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_cd853abd		I should not have pushed myself so hard these past days.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	283	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_7ac90ad5		The cough takes hold, and this time it does not let go.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	297	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_29a170ee		I sink to my knees on the wet road, the bag spilling open beside me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	297	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_df6bbc31		All that silver, scattered in the mud.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	297	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_04825213		What a waste.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	297	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_7ac90ad5_1		The cough takes hold, and this time it does not let go.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_2cecb16c		I stumble.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_6005ecf2		The road swims before my eyes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	309	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_d6998059_1		The road stretches ahead, quiet and grey beneath the morning cloud.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_1053f3a8		But for the first time in a very long while, I am not afraid of what lies at the end of it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_537462e0		I won't come home with one thousand pounds, not by far.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_f12d22bf		But I still managed to get something of value out of this adventure.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_e8bc324f		It will not last for ever. But it is enough to help you live a little longer, and a little better.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_01ed005a		Enough to hope.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	328	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_d95d0882		I keep walking.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	358	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_leave_744d8a30		There is nothing behind me worth turning back for.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	358	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_stay_92af2132		I press myself to the back of the hall as the footsteps grow closer.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	3	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_stay_ec5e3d9c		Ted Harring and Amelia Baxter descend the stairs and move through to the dining room without glancing my way.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	3	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_stay_890d61cf		I waste no time.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	3	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_stay_e59bddf1		The service stairs are at the far end of the corridor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	3	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_bd342c63		The attic corridor is narrow and very still.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_44c0f721		Dust on every surface.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_e2269a77		The staff quarters line the passage, their doors all shut.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_d9e120e9		No sound from behind any of them.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_cc281355		The whole house might as well be empty.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_5a26c0c3		At the far end of the hallway, I find the butler's room.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	29	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_ac4f4413		I have been here before.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	47	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_29495d75		The reinforced cabinet stands where it always stood, waiting.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	47	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_1add6041		I take the key from my pocket and fit it into the cabinet lock.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_11f34518		It turns without effort.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_47197cae		The doors swing open.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_bd9b1078		No bearer bonds. But then I never truly believed in those.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_c2439afa		The silver is real though.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_0fa89e91		A pair of candlesticks, a salver, a set of heavy serving spoons.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_b1279616		Not a fortune, by any standard. But it is something.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_838d1706		That will make this weekend a profitable one, at least.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_d1068110		I take what will fit without making my bag unmanageable.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_a97b2a43		Then I close the cabinet as best I can and step back.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_attic_b159a2e5		I ease the bedroom door closed behind me, and return to my room discreetly.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	57	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_room_grab_belongings_6e26341a		I gather my few belongings and get ready to leave.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	90	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_room_grab_belongings_97b2ed2e		My legs are weak. My chest aches.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	90	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_room_grab_belongings_0d07eeb5		If I attempt the walk to the village now, I will not make it. I know that.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	90	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_room_grab_belongings_e6183dee		I need to rest. Just a short nap before I make the journey.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	90	"[what]"
nurse_day3_morning_room_grab_belongings_3a02e4ca		I lock the door, lie fully clothed upon the bed, and close my eyes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/1_Morning/2_stay.rpy	90	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_6d303629		I am awakened by a noise.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_c131d3de		The front door, I can hear it from here.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_82ff5a33		It opens. It closes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_f8f3ff28		And after that, silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_f677ad1f		The silence of an empty house.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_10fb5ebb		I wait a little longer, counting my breaths.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_60bc53f6		Perhaps everyone else has left now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_adb783b8		I should go too.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	34	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_88f285c8		The entrance hall is deserted.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	54	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_7012894f		I cross to the window and glance at the drive.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	54	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_2bb5c193		No figures. No movement. Just the gravel and the grey sky beyond.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	54	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_c5fa6fdf		Good.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	54	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_d6e616c1		I check the weight of my bag — the candlesticks, the salver, the spoons.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_6fa5bfe3		All still there.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_327e15eb		I should leave now, while the way is clear.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	72	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_3e3743cf		But my stomach tightens with a familiar pang.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	72	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_0396fd4a		I have not eaten since yesterday evening, and the walk to the nearest village will be long.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	72	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_0544f163		The kitchen is just below. It would take only a few minutes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	72	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_b6cde6de		They leave.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_0bcaee78		I am alone with the plates.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_90070f91		Three places, three meals, all from the same pot.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_fc268b0e		And yet something stops me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_f8af55b9		A thought — quiet, persistent, impossible to dismiss.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_5afd6127		If someone has been killing the guests one by one, the food is the simplest means.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_c201a8c8		I have no proof. Only instinct, sharpened by years of watching people die.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_e11914e9		I look at my plate.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_5f92d907		Then at Mr Harring's.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_000f535e		If I am wrong, no harm done.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_f3336dc0		If I am right...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	88	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_f5e77015		I swap my plate with his.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	127	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_3c79ed09		Mr Harring stands and offers to help with the dishes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	135	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_c46a9ea5		But as he rises, something changes in his expression.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	135	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_bcf6dd4d		No.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_c510c60d		This is not my illness.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_9a84fa99		This is something else entirely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_e68639be		The food.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_f32db50c		There was never a safe choice.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_18ada185		I was dead the moment I sat down.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_c53eb4d2		The swap changed nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_7209f8c3		But the poison hasn't taken me yet.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_yes_66bc44fd		I look at Amelia Baxter	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_bcf6dd4d		No.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_27936e32		I am clearly being paranoid.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_76b72c38		I leave the plates where they are.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	178	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_a60e9447		I set down my fork.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	188	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_7dfa5df7		Something is wrong.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	188	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_fa93a6df		A wave of nausea rises from my stomach, sudden and sharp.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	196	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_fb6c9cf9		My vision swims.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	196	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_75260163		I grip the edge of the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	196	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_c6e92ce5	psychic	Miss Marsh? Are you quite all right?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	204	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_da69e507		I try to answer, but my tongue feels thick and heavy.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_d1f8be98		The room tilts.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_b2a05646		I know this feeling — not my illness, not the familiar ache in my chest.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_9a84fa99		This is something else entirely.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	208	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_63228970	nurse	The food...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	218	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_d3028f50	psychic	What about the food?	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	222	psychic "[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_bdf5fed8	nurse	It's been...	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	226	nurse "[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_deab76fc		I cannot finish the sentence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	230	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_16e49565		My legs give way beneath me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	230	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_25fcfe0e		My knees hit the floor.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_c6a9fb86		The cold of the stone rises through me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_b26f9cd4		Through the haze, I see Mr Harring rushing to my side.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_swap_no_1ed17e61		Miss Baxter is saying something, but the words are very far away now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_meal_1ab08342		They return, and we eat in silence.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_meal_09de6382		The food is plain but filling.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_meal_bd32e539		I watch the other two carefully, looking for any sign that something is amiss.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_meal_ffd26ecc		Nothing. We finish our meal without incident.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_meal_ba84ca3e		Perhaps I was being foolish after all.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	257	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_armed_5521adc7		I am on the floor now.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	279	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_armed_79568e50		The ceiling swims above me.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	279	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_0e8ba949		I lunge at her.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	291	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_73b278c5		It is a clumsy, desperate thing — more a stumble than an attack.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	291	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_6507d02a		But I catch her off guard and we both crash against the sideboard.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	291	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_533c076a		She pushes me back and I stagger, catching myself on the table's edge.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	301	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_22944320		The cough comes.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	307	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_a1755f8f		Not the small, manageable sort I have learnt to live with.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	307	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_fa253b2c		This is the deep, tearing kind that brings blood with it.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	307	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_190bdf0b		I double over, one hand pressed to my mouth, the other still gripping the table.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	307	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_f411b870		My body has nothing left to give.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_e4515fb5		The poison, the illness, the exertion — it is all catching up at once.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_day3_afternoon_confrontation_unarmed_3ba07b25		I slide to my knees.	game/scripts/nurse/Day 3/2_Afternoon/1_main.rpy	319	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_5fb96088		You pushed yourself beyond the limits of your endurance.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_168c216a		The illness that has been shadowing your every step finally claimed its due.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_e774a9f9		There was no one to hear your final, desperate cough.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_cdd5e6b2		No one to offer a glass of water, or a steadying hand.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_34f7a987		In the cold silence of the night, you were simply too tired to go on.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_exhausted_fbe1cf38		Perhaps if you had managed your strength from the start, the outcome might have been different.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	8	"[what]"
nurse_ending_billiard_room_death_ac46f7fc		You confronted a dangerous man, alone.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	32	"[what]"
nurse_ending_billiard_room_death_89e9a455		In a room without witnesses.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	32	"[what]"
nurse_ending_billiard_room_death_63fae1e4		Already weakened by a deadly disease, the shock was enough to be the end of you.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	32	"[what]"
nurse_ending_billiard_room_death_dee468a3		You died on the floor, your accusations still warm on your lips.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	32	"[what]"
nurse_ending_poisoned_123d102a		You collapsed on the floor, and died there.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	52	"[what]"
nurse_ending_poisoned_d24dd843		You swapped plates, thinking yourself clever.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	58	"[what]"
nurse_ending_poisoned_6e5e2cea		But that didn't help your fate.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	58	"[what]"
nurse_ending_poisoned_341b3a4c		You suspected the food, but chose not to act.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_ending_poisoned_18363a5b		So your fate was sealed.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	66	"[what]"
nurse_ending_gunned_down_2c30d22f		You went to a great deal of trouble to find a gun and the bullets to load it.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	82	"[what]"
nurse_ending_gunned_down_f1a2859b		But that didn't change a thing.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	82	"[what]"
nurse_ending_gunned_down_dd79c396		In the confusion, the weapon turned against you.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	82	"[what]"
nurse_ending_gunned_down_f210b2c7		A firearm is dangerous for those who don't know how to handle one.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	82	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_c7f99f4a		You escaped the manor, but the night swallowed you whole.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_87f2fcc1		Lost in the woods, cold and exhausted, you sat down to rest and never rose again.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_a6adccb4		They found you the next morning, curled beneath an oak, frost on your eyelashes.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_a45aa7b9		You saw the truth — Lady Claythorn fleeing her own house — and it should have told you everything.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_537853cf		Don't wait too long.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_at_night_682c329e		Leave this place as fast as you can.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	102	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_poor_b5910abb		You escaped, but took very little with you.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	126	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_poor_7a934d5b		Clearly not enough to make a difference to your finances.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	126	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_poor_679b932f		You can forget the dreams of vacations in the sun.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	126	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_poor_2f4682f2		Yet, you are better off than those who stayed.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	126	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_poor_ea34def7		Not the ideal ending, but not the worst either, I suppose.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	126	"[what]"
nurse_ending_psychic_fight_death_1fece62f		You fought back — unarmed, poisoned, and already half-dead.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	148	"[what]"
nurse_ending_psychic_fight_death_565ce5fe		It was never going to be enough.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	148	"[what]"
nurse_ending_psychic_fight_death_d157b447		The poison had already done its work, and the struggle finished what remained.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	148	"[what]"
nurse_ending_psychic_fight_death_4e530d9e		You died on the dining room floor, still reaching for the woman who killed you.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	148	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_cdd0238d		You made it past the gate and onto the road.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_738bef1f		For a while, the cold air and the promise of freedom kept you moving.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_762608be		But your body had nothing left to give.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_538b9a2b		The cough came first, then the weakness in your legs, then the ground.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_803e4b3b		They found you the next morning, face down in the mud.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_collapse_69bdb95a		So close. But not close enough.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	168	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_rich_ce039213		You escaped, and you took enough with you to make a real difference.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	192	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_rich_8d001883		That's about as good as this weekend could have ended.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	192	"[what]"
nurse_ending_escape_rich_e077a367		As long as you don't think too hard about what happened to the others.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_endings.rpy	192	"[what]"
nurse_generic_weather_saturday_morning_65ed0621	nurse	This night was dreadful, wasn't it?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	18	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_weather_saturday_morning_24e32178	nurse	I couldn't sleep at all.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	18	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_weather_saturday_evening_2c3dcc30	nurse	The weather is much better today than it was last night.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	29	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_weather_saturday_evening_4b85bee4	nurse	Hopefully I shall sleep better tonight.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	29	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_room_d75519a1	nurse	My room is named after "Queen Alexandra."	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	46	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_room_bee03412	nurse	Like the queen mother, I believe.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	46	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_age_eb3f6fd4	nurse	I am 42 years old.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_age_07c0e78a	nurse	It's hard to believe really.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_age_2afeb09e	nurse	I don't feel that old at all.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_1d67c332	nurse	Oh well, the most obvious thing about me is that I am a nurse.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	74	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_fec489ca	nurse	I started young and served in various wars.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	74	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_1c6f60db	nurse	In peacetime, I usually took a job at a hospital.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	74	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_37e7cf0a	nurse	Now I mostly nurse the elderly.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	74	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_68e9d2c1	psychic	In an old person's facility?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	84	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_40b83ab2	nurse	No, not like that. I mostly assist wealthier individuals who require special in-house assistance.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	88	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_4dda19a0	psychic	Are you taking care of someone at the moment?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	92	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_364e8c7e	nurse	Not right now.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	96	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_8d66f854	nurse	And perhaps after I receive this prize, I won't have to.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	96	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_d45f09b7	nurse	Nursing is an amazing job that I love,	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	96	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_847237f7	nurse	but it can be exhausting.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	96	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_psychic_3625a96a	psychic	Yes, one can imagine.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	106	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_1d67c332	nurse	Oh well, the most obvious thing about me is that I am a nurse.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	117	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_fec489ca	nurse	I started young and served in various wars.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	117	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_706e9518	nurse	In peacetime, ....	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	117	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_aa56dd8b	doctor	Wait a minute, in which wars did you actually serve?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	125	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_19433604	nurse	Well, the Great War, and before that I was...	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	129	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_93597cd7	doctor	Sorry, to interrupt, but I think I remember you now.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	133	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_c8d121e3	doctor	Were you in China during the Boxer's Rebellion by chance?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	133	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_306206b2	nurse	I was indeed, I wouldn't think you would remember me.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	139	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_88bebae1	doctor	Right, so we did work together.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	143	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_00de076c	doctor	Why didn't you say something?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	143	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_b40867d7	nurse	I didn't want to presume.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	149	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_c7688eb7	nurse	I was a young nurse among many.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	149	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_ad81fc90	nurse	And it was a very long time ago.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	149	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_e4500274	doctor	It was indeed.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	159	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_d45efadf	doctor	But it is nice to see again.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	159	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_background_doctor_08518548	nurse	Likewise.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	165	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_ac80dd57	nurse	Well, I don't wish to sound boastful.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	174	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_908ec3ab	nurse	But I've been told I'm the nurse who's served in the most wars in the whole country, apparently.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	174	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_ebd44d2f	doctor	Truly? You kept going, even after everything that happened in China?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	180	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_d1b4cf5c	nurse	Indeed. I daresay some would have lost heart after what happened there.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	184	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_38385743	nurse	But not me. It only strengthened my belief that nursing was my true calling.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	184	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_7863a3df	nurse	When I returned to England, I kept volunteering wherever I was needed.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	184	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_8c2b4d6f	doctor	Then you must have witnessed a great many conflicts.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	192	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_a8ae836c	nurse	Yes. Before the Boxer Rebellion, there was the Cretan Revolt.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	196	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_86129e52	nurse	And afterwards, several others — until, of course, the last one.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	196	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_d1733a83	nurse	Which I rather think will be the last for me.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	196	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_97ea097f	doctor	We all hoped it would be the last for everyone.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	204	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_0e96a7ac	doctor	But I fear war is not likely to vanish from the world just yet.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	204	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_56e11948	nurse	No, I'm not so naïve as to think so.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	210	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_2d080eb6	nurse	But one can at least hope that nothing as dreadful as the Great War will ever come again.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	210	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_doctor_a93f61fd	doctor	I sincerely hope you're right, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	216	doctor "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_e2367840	nurse	It is nothing special, really.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	227	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_c5532e4f	nurse	But it turns out I am the nurse who served in the most wars in the whole country, apparently.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	227	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_9438b909	psychic	Oh my, that is extraordinary.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	233	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_b3c38c70	psychic	But how many wars did you serve in?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	233	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_f036bbfc	nurse	There have been quite a few, that's true.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_ec08a5b2	nurse	I started my career really early during the Cretan Revolt, where I was stationed on a British frigate.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_806b26ba	nurse	But I truly experienced the horror of war for the first time during the Boxer Rebellion of 1899.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_2457abc9	nurse	The brutality of the combats, then later, the lives they left behind made an impression that would last my whole life.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_125afa4c	nurse	Afterwards, I followed the army again in small engagements in India.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_ca5fae6a	nurse	When the Great War started, I thought at first that I was too old to go.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_6446206e	nurse	But the atrocities I kept hearing about left me no choice.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_ba6fd745	nurse	I had to be there to help.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_9bfd2631	nurse	It's what I do.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_169274c9	nurse	So I joined again and lasted throughout the whole duration of the war.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	239	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_heroic_act_psychic_7137bf9e	psychic	How commendable.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	261	psychic "[what]"
nurse_generic_manor_15de41e3	nurse	It's a grand house.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_generic_manor_72018ff7	nurse	I've been in many houses of the same style, but none so big or impressive.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_choices.rpy	272	nurse "[what]"
nurse_bedroom_default_3512255f		No answer.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	5	"[what]"
nurse_bedroom_default_intro_37288ccd	nurse	Hello? Is anyone there?	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	18	nurse "[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_79805797		The door is locked.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	36	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_6d606083		But it would take me very little effort to open it.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_a4a57afd		In my years of nursing, I have become acquainted with all manner of locks — on medicine cabinets, ward doors, and supply rooms.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_7ddbb683		And I quickly realised how convenient it is to be able to open them all.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_5f02171b		That is why I learned to pick locks.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_943e702b		A most useful skill.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_04ab4896		So, I easily make my way inside.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	44	"[what]"
nurse_lockpick_door_558d1d0a		I easily make my way inside.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	60	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_198d9fd4		The room is neat to the point of severity.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_12ff96b1		A coat hangs straight on its hook.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_39aa514a		A leather case sits packed on the stand, its straps buckled precisely.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_fa77745d		Nothing is left in reach.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_501b5209		Military discipline of this kind belongs to one man in this house.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_a5e5da89		I search thoroughly, but find nothing of use.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_default_991c3ca5		Whatever the Captain values, he keeps it close to his person.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	74	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_again_a476310a		I look over the Captain's immaculate room one last time.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_again_abbafc0a		Everything remains exactly as I found it earlier.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_again_2ea8e3e5		If there is a secret here, it is too well hidden for me to find now.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	99	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_again_208572e1		I should not linger and press my luck.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	99	"[what]"
