nurse_search_captain_master_key_97fd1e3a		The hunting jacket — heavier than the dinner jacket, rougher cloth.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_340f130d		I slip my hand into the right pocket.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_9850f53c		Nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_37f3c848		The left.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_427fe318		My fingers close around cold metal.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_543dbad4		A key, heavy and old, with a long shaft and an open bit at the end.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_d2d3c725		It doesn't look like a normal bedroom key.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_f95a92ca		That must be the butler's master key.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_captain_master_key_da2e2514		This might come in handy.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	114	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_fb45dddc		The room is larger than mine, dressed in pale silks and heavy curtains.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_b931238c		This is unquestionably the lady of the house's own chamber.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_f2195e14		I look quickly through the dressing table.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_569778cf		A jet brooch, a few hairpins, a string of pearls in a velvet case.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_daaa8803		They catch my eye for a moment — but only for a moment.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	146	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_4847ef94		This is not much for a woman of Lady Claythorn's standing.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_368cb8b4		Pearls and jet are for show — for evenings and guests.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_123fc33a		There should be more.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_fc1eab50		I also don't see the prize money anywhere. That's the real reason I am in this room.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_476a1e40		One thousand pounds each. Seven guests. Seven thousand pounds in bearer bonds.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_5f8a053b		Whoever holds bearer bonds holds the money. There are no names on them. No register.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_d41e036b		They could walk out of this house in anyone's pocket.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_b47fc8bd		But that is if they exist at all.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_9ada17b2		It would not surprise me greatly if there were no bonds. No ceremony. Nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_a07962a5		But if they are real, they are here somewhere.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_046f202c		I look more carefully. Behind the curtain, beneath the floorboards, behind a picture — it could be anywhere.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_30e5c8cb		But I find nothing.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_5b3e5f26		There is a safe somewhere. There must be.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_117b8965		Though perhaps not here. A woman like Lady Claythorn may well keep it in a study, or some other room she considers entirely her own.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_a98f0c1c		I simply have not found it yet.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_61ed2b69		Before I leave, I look over what might be worth taking.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_default_e7a1833f		The pearls are the only items of any real value.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	160	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_again_98c0cb42		I carefully search Lady Claythorn's room once more.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	205	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_again_793203e0		The heavy curtains, the dressing table, the floorboards... I check it all again.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	205	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_again_d5a59de0		But there is simply nothing else to be found.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	205	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_again_fee85a62		If the bearer bonds are here, they are in a safe I cannot locate.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	205	"[what]"
nurse_search_host_again_e7b1d493		The string of pearls still sits in its velvet case on the dressing table.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	217	"[what]"
nurse_take_pearls_ed98fb36		Not first-rate, but they will fetch something.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_take_pearls_74708fa8		I slip them into my bag and leave.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	238	"[what]"
nurse_search_lad_default_b8a3d5e7		There isn't much in here.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	253	"[what]"
nurse_search_lad_default_710d7734		A jacket thrown over the chair, a battered holdall on the floor.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	253	"[what]"
nurse_search_lad_default_67532b89		There is nothing here worth taking.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	253	"[what]"
nurse_search_lad_default_b1bf22df		But it should not be a surprise.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	253	"[what]"
nurse_search_lad_default_254086da		Anyone looking more than a few seconds at Ted Harring would see he is not a man of means.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	253	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_738eceb7		Mr Moody's room.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_6fc063a6		His body settled on the bed, hidden underneath the bed sheets.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_9863c688		One could be easily frightened, but I am used to this.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_c51d4516		Usually, a dead body doesn't cause me anguish, only respect and sadness.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_4b9fbbee		And yet here I am, with the purpose of stealing from a man who can't defend himself anymore.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_603a8be1		I should feel bad, but I know I need the money more than he does now.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_2ede356c		So I start looking.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_1d119881		But the bounty is meager.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_00023fa8		Nothing on the dressing table.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_31f7622b		A small case with his clothes under the bed.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_2fac8ceb		That's it.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_8014562a		I could also search his body, but that would be going too far, even for me.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
nurse_search_broken_default_0068ec95		I close the door softly and leave.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	274	"[what]"
