nurse_gun_room_default_f8e8707a		The small pistols are still available if I so desire.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	373	"[what]"
nurse_gun_room_default_1cf4e0a3		The gun room.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	383	"[what]"
nurse_gun_room_default_8b3bd454		I am certain that I should not be here, so I made sure no one noticed me.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	383	"[what]"
nurse_gun_room_default_560c51ee		Shotguns and hunting rifles line three walls, arranged on open racks.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	383	"[what]"
nurse_gun_room_default_06177e2e		The smell of gun oil is sharp.	game/scripts/nurse/nurse_generic_locations.rpy	383	"[what]"
