psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_388c8c4a	psychic	I am afraid it is important.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_575b1140	psychic	Might you let me in? It will not take long.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	83	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_9d3f7a74	nurse	Very well, do come in.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	89	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_cceda66a	nurse	What can I do for you?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	97	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_9a726ca1	psychic	Nothing, rather the reverse.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	101	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_25190848	psychic	I am sorry to intrude, but I noticed the blood on your handkerchief.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	101	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_813ce950	psychic	I wondered whether there is anything I can do to help.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	101	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_fa92ca03	nurse	I suppose I could not have hidden it forever.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	109	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_5bc4baea	nurse	You see, I am suffering from a most serious disease.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	109	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_7b6c5ecc	nurse	One for which there is no known cure. Consumption.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	109	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_8857688e		Another racking cough takes her.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	119	"[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_e1333528	psychic	I am so very sorry.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	125	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_218e3603	psychic	When did you learn of it?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	125	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_089e0c51	nurse	A couple of years ago.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	131	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_3d48dc39	nurse	And if I am to trust my doctor, I have perhaps a year at most.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	131	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_fd410b1e	psychic	My goodness, how horrible.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	137	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_5f003282	psychic	Is there anything at all I can do?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	137	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_ef1ba994	nurse	There is nothing to be done.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_ee84e7c3	nurse	My doctor has prescribed a strong draught that I must take before bed.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_c27d7371	nurse	It usually helps me to sleep.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_d30d9722	nurse	At times I must take it during the day, which is why I am so often in my room, resting.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_0e0d261b	nurse	But you should go now. I shall try to sleep a little before dinner.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_b8f44060	nurse	Thank you for your kindness.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	143	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_d49a3688	psychic	Of course. I shall go.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	157	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_insist_5dd7ece7	nurse	Thank you.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	161	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_ignore_c4c8c176	psychic	It can wait, of course. Goodbye, Miss Marsh.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	174	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_no_hunt_bedroom_nurse_ignore_c8d126c7	nurse	Goodbye, Miss Baxter.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_bedroom_nurse.rpy	178	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_e3cbda4b		I am the first to arrive, so I pick a table and wait for Rosalind Marsh.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	5	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_eae4ade9		I am seated comfortably, lost in my thoughts when she enters the room.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	5	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_319ab6d9	psychic	Miss Marsh, would you like to join me?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	13	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_2995f230	nurse	Yes, thank you.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	17	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_7256cbdf	psychic	It seems we haven't really had a chance to talk yet, right?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	21	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_3c4a8002		Suddenly, a staff member walks in.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	27	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_e38fe3a1	maid	Excuse me for interrupting, but do you ladies need some lunch?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	31	maid "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_6013b815	nurse	That would be lovely, thank you.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	35	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_fd51d282		After a few minutes, she returns with some plates.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	41	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_e94e7db6		As we eat, we chat about trivial matters.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	41	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_ec6e1792		When our lunch is over, Rosalind rises from her seat.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	49	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_b8b67713		She lets out a painful cough.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	55	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_6bb1cedd	nurse	I'm feeling rather poorly.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_3198cfb8	nurse	I think I will retire to my room.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_ea4c3888	nurse	Would you mind being left on your own?	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	59	nurse "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_eb4738c3	psychic	Not at all, please don't concern yourself.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	67	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_327f8a5d	psychic	There is more than enough here to occupy me.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	67	psychic "[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_bd6ce876		With the manor so quiet, I might seize the chance to explore unnoticed.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	73	"[what]"
psychic_day2_hunt_tea_room_880e1a5a		And perhaps I should call upon Rosalind Marsh later, to see how she is doing.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/2_No Hunt/2_tea_room.rpy	73	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_garden_1b94f8d8		I reach the large hall and prepare to open the door.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	119	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_garden_ba655696		The weather has improved, but it is pitch dark outside.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	119	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_garden_2564b169		What possessed me? There is no reason to go out now.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	119	"[what]"
