psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_3e576929		Cautiously, I step inside and see Doctor Baldwin's body.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	219	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_06bfbc73		He is lying peacefully in his bed.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	229	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_doctor_55d21ca3		Unsure what I could do here, I decide to leave.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	229	"[what]"
psychic_day2_bedroom_broken_already_see_e6bfd41e		I stand once again in front of Thomas Moody's room.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	266	"[what]"
psychic_day2_bedroom_broken_already_see_dc181cca		I do not know what compelled me to come here again.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	266	"[what]"
psychic_day2_bedroom_broken_already_see_6c45a02a		I try to open the door, but I can't. The memory of his dead body is still too fresh in my mind.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	266	"[what]"
psychic_day2_bedroom_broken_already_see_6082bb32		I'd better go somewhere else.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	266	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_93b13dfa		I knock on the door.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	286	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_871a2394	drunk	Grrr, Mrrrr, Errrr	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	290	drunk "[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_dfdb42f4		I recognise Samuel Manning's voice, and it's clear he is too drunk to be coherent.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	294	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_bedroom_drunk_e02ddb6e		Since the door is locked, I decide not to interfere.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	294	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_attic_default_7405578b		I am back in the attic.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	315	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_attic_default_1f473a41		But it seems there is nobody now.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	315	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_attic_default_728cf243		Maybe it's too late.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	315	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_attic_default_8f8a9e75		I climb the stairs to the attic and arrive in a dimly lit hallway.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	325	"[what]"
psychic_day2_evening_attic_default_e857dc25		There are multiple doors, most of them lie in darkness.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 2/3_Evening/0_map_choices.rpy	325	"[what]"
