psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_70e27dfd		He turns back towards me.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_08d2ac89		There is blood on his hands.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
