psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_0ae2e8b4		He tries to take a step in my direction, but collapses on the ground.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_e08e8950		When I realise what is happening, I quickly decide I can't stay here for long.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_5ea695a7		So I leave the Captain behind and start to run as fast as I can.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_9c9ab626		I try to catch up with Ted Harring, but he is already so far away that I can't even see him.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	125	"[what]"
