psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_e58b5c5c		I go as fast as I can but I don't see Ted Harring until I reach the town.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	155	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_6ac39e82		I head straight to the police station and there he is.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	155	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_9e39f34f		When I enter, he looks embarrassed to see me.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	155	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_98bb6f29		Probably feeling the weight of the guilt of leaving me to an uncertain fate.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	155	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_2f2f4490		But I am glad he made it anyway.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	167	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_e2feca1a		I hug him and tell him about Captain Sinha.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	167	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_3ced706b		He replies that officers are on their way to Claythorn Manor.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	167	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_escape_f60b6b5c		We wait for them for a long time.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2b_escape.rpy	167	"[what]"
