psychic_day3_afternoon_stay_68cc4749		He looks anxious to do something.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	25	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_stay_2dc0c3fa		But as he stands, he suddenly looks dizzy.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	25	"[what]"
