psychic_day3_afternoon_gun_death_bef5c067		When I look upon the dead body, the room spins, I am overwhelmed with guilt and disbelief.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	70	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_gun_death_b0f9c9c8		As I feel myself falling, I attempt to grasp the table but end up catching the tablecloth instead.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	70	"[what]"
