psychic_day3_afternoon_gun_death_d087fdb3		I try to stand up but injure my hands on a shard of glass.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	84	"[what]"
psychic_day3_afternoon_gun_death_61b10655		Once again, I fall onto my back.	game/scripts/psychic/Day 3/2_Afternoon/2_stay.rpy	84	"[what]"
