common_day2_morning_host_death_29ab908c	host	He will likely tell us more later.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	34	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_245e865b		She then sits down in her chair.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	40	"[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_9ee81a4b		Everyone looks shaken up.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	40	"[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_a817f93e	captain	How terrible.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	46	captain "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_d854879c	psychic	Yes, such sad news.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	50	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_1693a62c		We continue eating slowly in silence for a moment when the doctor enters the room.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	54	"[what]"
