common_day2_morning_host_death_doctor_68a0183e	doctor	I can't say anything definitive for now.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	67	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_death_doctor_2aca9fba	doctor	But it's very likely a natural death, possibly triggered by an old wound from the war.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	67	doctor "[what]"
