common_day2_morning_host_death_doctor_913c071b		Nobody speaks much.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	86	"[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_db7a5a70	host	Well, as I mentioned earlier, activities were planned for today.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	101	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_a6b31717	host	This morning, those who wished to were supposed to go on a hunt.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	101	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_3e3bc0b8	host	A sad event has happened, but it's not a reason to remain idle.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	101	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_ed09e8ce	host	So, if no one objects, I propose that we continue according to what was planned.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	101	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_367cabb6		A faint murmur of assent passes through the room.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	111	"[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_bca27853	host	Excellent.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	115	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_1c9dcb91	host	Everything is ready for those who wish to join the hunt.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	115	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_5d06ae5f	host	I know most of you are probably not accustomed to this type of event.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	115	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_host_hunt_70247bd5	host	That's why our staff can lend you everything you'll need—clothes, guns—and they will also assist you throughout the event.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	115	host "[what]"
