common_day2_morning_host_hunt_d57e16bd	host	You can relax and enjoy the warmth of the house until the others return.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	115	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_captain_drunk_7026c60a	captain	I will come.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	136	captain "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_captain_drunk_2a642215	captain	What has happened today is tragic, but there is no point in lingering here.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	136	captain "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_captain_drunk_3bf8a922	drunk	I'll... come too.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	142	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_captain_drunk_1eacc043	drunk	Fresh air will do me well.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	142	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_psychic_4af20352	psychic	I am sorry, but I would rather not.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	152	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_psychic_5411fca0	psychic	If you do not mind, I should prefer to remain indoors.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	152	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_psychic_374bcc3b	psychic	Please do not let me stand in your way.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	152	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_nurse_7d318fda	nurse	I feel the same as Miss Baxter, I'm afraid.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	164	nurse "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_nurse_60d6a491	nurse	I should not know what to do with a gun.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	164	nurse "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_nurse_9dfd8a62	host	Of course, I understand.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	170	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_nurse_2440130c	host	I shall make sure you are comfortable staying inside.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	170	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_nurse_08834e1d	host	And how do you feel, Mister Harring?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	170	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_host_to_doctor_ec4ccdaf	host	Very good. What about you, Doctor Baldwin?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	182	host "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_lad_a6a66c16	lad	I'll... I'll come too, of course.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	190	lad "[what]"
common_day2_morning_hunt_end_80846c64	host	Those of you who are going may change and then fetch a weapon downstairs.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	198	host "[what]"
