common_day2_morning_lad_psychic_aed14fe4	psychic	I was wondering if everyone would join us on time.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	219	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_lad_psychic_41f8c29d	psychic	There are still a few people missing.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	219	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_lad_psychic_6c8baac9	psychic	For instance, I don't think we'll see Mr Manning anytime soon.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	219	psychic "[what]"
common_day2_morning_lad_psychic_69d4c3df	psychic	He was so drunk yesterday that I wouldn't be surprised if he doesn't show up before noon.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/1_main.rpy	219	psychic "[what]"
