common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_dea81d00	host	Dead?!!!	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	79	host surprised "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_41eebcb6	host	How is that possible?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	79	host surprised "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_b5ce6c4d	doctor	I'm not sure yet. I'll need to examine him further.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	85	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_016df550	doctor	Best if you stepped out for this.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	85	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_3fe27dd4	doctor	I'll return downstairs once I know more.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	85	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_1aa5f70d	butler	Please, My Lady—this way.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	93	butler "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_e6247181	host	Oh... Yes, of course...	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	97	host "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_ed11da7a		The butler escorts Lady Claythorn out.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	106	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_f8e953ef		The doctor turns to face me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	106	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_706910da		Lady Claythorn and the butler leave,	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	114	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_9f44566d		leaving me alone with Ted Harring.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	114	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_f199c78b		Why did he come up here?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	114	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_35f95baa	doctor	Mr Harring, may I ask—why are you here?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	122	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_ce19e77c	lad	I was just... I thought I might...	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	126	lad "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_dc778422	doctor	Never mind. Since you're here, you can help.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	130	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_ae348cdc	doctor	Let's turn him over and check for injuries.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	130	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_42f40941		He examines the body carefully for some time.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	138	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_2f61b4f6		I feel somewhat uneasy. Before me lies the body of a man who was rather cross with me the last time we spoke.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	148	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_c18bb698		And now he is dead.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	148	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_08a7b770		Well, it is not the first time that has happened to me, and I daresay it will not be the last.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	148	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_d3c0876d		Still, I cannot help feeling bad about it.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	148	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_1f3c2af2		I examine the body carefully for signs of foul play. Nothing obvious.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_bfed0f02		Rigor mortis has set in—quite early.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_b6a68746		Which suggests he died shortly after going to bed.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_821207dd		Not unusual, in itself.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_b87a9f88		Normally, I'd remove the mask for closer observation...	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_585f37c7		But it feels wrong. Perhaps best left to the coroner.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	158	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_7182c0fe		Yet something's nagging at me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	174	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_f56ce013		That book I read yesterday—how did the victim die?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	180	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_da79871f		Strychnine poisoning.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	180	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_a073206b		Probably coincidence, but one of the telltale signs is early rigor mortis.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	180	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_328862b0		Others include: blue lips, frothing at the mouth, and a twisted expression.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	180	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_550af621		All visible—if I remove the mask.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	180	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_2a635ab4		After discovering the letter in Samuel Manning's room yesterday, it is difficult to regard this as mere coincidence.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	194	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_2382e9c9		I had assumed I was the only person in danger, but that may not be the case.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	194	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_2a54a2ab		The very thought sends a chill through me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	194	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_host_14721061		In such circumstances, I shall be forgiven for treating this death as something other than natural.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	194	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_keep_mask_73f655da		I leave the mask in place.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	222	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_keep_mask_7314e0fe		No sense in stirring up more trouble.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	222	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_keep_mask_bbb49f9c		I've got enough to go on for now.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	222	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_15ded20c	lad	What do you think happened, Doctor?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	237	lad "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_f1e85c78	doctor	I'm not certain.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_a9c18431	doctor	He seemed in reasonable health.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_2c4c7557	doctor	But war injuries can be unpredictable.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_1abd8885	doctor	Some patients are stable for years, then... sudden failure.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	241	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_b9b55295	lad	So it was natural?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	251	lad "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_63b6e95e	doctor	Possibly. But I can't be sure.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_af4944b2	doctor	Nothing can be ruled out.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_eec68412	doctor	We'll need a post-mortem to know for certain.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_c3cac404	doctor	First, we should contact the authorities.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	255	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_cfc14fda		He leaves the room.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	267	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_09864438		I follow him back to the dining room.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	267	"[what]"
common_day2_breakfast_follow_doctor_lad_normal_7dbbc849		We both head back downstairs.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/1_Morning/2_follow.rpy	275	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_butler_groups_b5411c95	butler	Good, now that everyone is ready, I propose we split into two groups.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/1_main.rpy	3	butler "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_butler_groups_f18e9239	butler	It will be easier to spot game that way.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/1_main.rpy	3	butler "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_footman_1_05a1a82c	footman	Alright, if everyone's ready, we can continue.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	3	footman "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_footman_1_097dc975	footman	Hopefully, we'll have better luck this time.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	3	footman "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_498d2a19	drunk	Oh, a rabbit!	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	16	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_018fe684		He cocks his gun, shaking slightly.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	22	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_0943f76b		Then, he fires.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	22	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_0ded0b7e		He missed by a long way.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	36	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_5a8627dd		By the time I could try again, the rabbit had bolted.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	36	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_71d1ac4f		I'm frustrated, but then I hear a cry.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	36	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_69ff4253		A sharp pain irradiates through my stomach.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	46	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_b0b9d553		My legs give way and I fall to the ground.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	46	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_a0899d9b		I allowed myself a moment of distraction and he seized it.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	54	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_446acbb2		Bloody hell.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	54	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_0c763d10		Bloody hell, the fool has shot me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	62	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_1bd88f0b		I turn and see Doctor Baldwin crying out in pain on the ground.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	68	"[what]"
