common_day2_hunt_accident_death_f2ef26a0		I turn to the footman.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	94	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_4c20257f	lad	Hurry, fetch the others.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	98	lad "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_47f98eca	footman	Yes, of course, sir.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	102	footman "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_f6b8f550	drunk	Oh no, what have I done?!	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	106	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_27fd3d03	drunk	It was an accident.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	106	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_6d3223d5	drunk	I never intended this. Please believe me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	106	drunk "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_ac9e23b4		I ignore Samuel Manning entirely and crouch beside the doctor.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	116	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_c21cdf23		I have no idea how to help him.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	116	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_e1bdde5e		But he will know what to do.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	116	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_eddd49f7		He avoids my gaze, feigning remorse.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	128	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_b77f607e		Yet I can see the truth in his eyes.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	128	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_5930facf		He is delighted.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	128	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_c693ece7		I was a fool to let him anywhere near me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	128	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_cd84b87b		He stands there trembling, shame washing over his face.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	140	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_d940585a		There is something else in his expression, yet I cannot place it.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	140	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_b5e2d618		But there is no time for that now.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	146	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_8ad45b92		I must act quickly.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	146	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_9ff9952e		I call out to Ted Harring.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	146	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_fca1f400	doctor	Quickly, remove my shirt.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	154	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_ca513b60	doctor	I need to see where the bullet went in.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	154	doctor "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_be4746ee		My hands shake as I tear open his shirt.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	162	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_672783cf		Blood has soaked through the fabric.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	162	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_8c25c4d5		I see a small hole on his right side.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	162	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_01d7574a		At first glance, it does not appear too dreadful.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	162	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_a9acfe06		The lad helps me remove my shirt as best he can, though he is shaking like a leaf.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	174	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_a72b015d	lad	I found the wound.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	178	lad "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_d8dd543e	lad	Do you want me to press on it?	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	178	lad "[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_a140313f		The doctor inspects it himself.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	186	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_8ddffd3e		A look of dread washes over his face.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	186	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_be6fecbd		I look down at the small, neat hole in my abdomen.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	194	"[what]"
