common_day2_hunt_accident_death_3c1da7bb		Of all the places it could strike, it had to be the liver.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	194	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_735724c0		Damn it.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	194	"[what]"
