common_day2_hunt_accident_death_ae8a8916		He looks towards Samuel Manning with pure hatred, yet says nothing aloud.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	228	"[what]"
common_day2_hunt_accident_death_e1a681ce		Filled with anger, I turn my eyes upon the man who has shot me.	game/scripts/_common/Day 2/2_Hunt/2_accident.rpy	234	"[what]"
